(21, 550, 8.44, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pB8BM7pdSp6B6Ih7QZ4DrQ3PmJK.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hZkgoQYus5vegHoetLkCJzb17zJ.jpg', 'en', 'Fight Club', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'A ticking-time-bomb insomniac and a slippery soap salesman channel primal male aggression into a shocking new form of therapy. Their concept catches on, with underground \"fight clubs\" forming in every town, until an eccentric gets in the way and ignites an out-of-control spiral toward oblivion.', '1999-10-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dfeUzm6KF4g', 'David Fincher', 'Edward Norton, Brad Pitt, Helena Bonham Carter, Meat Loaf, Jared Leto'),
