(132, 600, 8.134, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kMKyx1k8hWWscYFnPbnxxN4Eqo4.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mKEmuB7diOa7Ef0tJSGQ3fYJnNe.jpg', 'en', 'Full Metal Jacket', 'Drama', 'War', NULL, 'A pragmatic U.S. Marine observes the dehumanizing effects the U.S.-Vietnam War has on his fellow recruits from their brutal boot camp training to the bloody street fighting in Hue.', '1987-06-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZFlm7fFfEmU', 'Stanley Kubrick', 'Matthew Modine, Adam Baldwin, Vincent D\'Onofrio, R. Lee Ermey, Dorian Harewood'),
(133, 470044, 8.132, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2icwBom0t5nmOuZI9FVXF3gkMK0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kH8xW7K2Gp1KOXoeewcLPkfqZ8K.jpg', 'en', 'The Hate U Give', 'Crime', 'Drama', NULL, 'Raised in a poverty-stricken slum, a 16-year-old girl named Starr now attends a suburban prep school. After she witnesses a police officer shoot her unarmed best friend, she\'s torn between her two very different worlds as she tries to speak her truth.', '2018-10-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3MM8OkVT0hw', 'George Tillman Jr.', 'Amandla Stenberg, Regina Hall, Russell Hornsby, K.J. Apa, Common'),
(134, 508442, 8.13, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hm58Jw4Lw8OIeECIq5qyPYhAeRJ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rQaHA74pevnGsxcKGaoZVGWe9TC.jpg', 'en', 'Soul', 'Animation', 'Family', 'Comedy', 'Joe Gardner is a middle school teacher with a love for jazz music. After a successful audition at the Half Note Club, he suddenly gets into an accident that separates his soul from his body and is transported to the You Seminar, a center in which souls develop and gain passions before being transported to a newborn child. Joe must enlist help from the other souls-in-training, like 22, a soul who has spent eons in the You Seminar, in order to get back to Earth.', '2020-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gs--6c7Hn_A', 'Pete Docter', 'Jamie Foxx, Tina Fey, Graham Norton, Rachel House, Alice Braga'),
(135, 500, 8.1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xi8Iu6qyTfyZVDVy60raIOYJJmk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jqFjgNnxpXIXWuPsyfqmcLXRo9p.jpg', 'en', 'Reservoir Dogs', 'Crime', 'Thriller', NULL, 'A botched robbery indicates a police informant, and the pressure mounts in the aftermath at a warehouse. Crime begets violence as the survivors -- veteran Mr. White, newcomer Mr. Orange, psychopathic parolee Mr. Blonde, bickering weasel Mr. Pink and Nice Guy Eddie -- unravel.', '1992-09-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2KLZ4fSXtgI', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Harvey Keitel, Tim Roth, Michael Madsen, Chris Penn, Steve Buscemi'),
(136, 531428, 8.125, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2LquGwEhbg3soxSCs9VNyh5VJd9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/foFq1RZWQIgFuCQ0nyYccywjFyX.jpg', 'fr', 'Portrait of a Lady on Fire', 'Drama', 'Romance', 'History', 'On an isolated island in Brittany at the end of the eighteenth century, a female painter is obliged to paint a wedding portrait of a young woman.', '2019-09-18', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-fQPTwma9o', 'Céline Sciamma', 'Noémie Merlant, Adèle Haenel, Luàna Bajrami, Valeria Golino, Armande Boulanger'),
(137, 600354, 8.124, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pr3bEQ517uMb5loLvjFQi8uLAsp.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/h3weAFgg06GqchI2xDfufBgSFTj.jpg', 'en', 'The Father', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'A man refuses all assistance from his daughter as he ages and, as he tries to make sense of his changing circumstances, he begins to doubt his loved ones, his own mind and even the fabric of his reality.', '2020-12-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g0ox9ExOA1M', 'Florian Zeller', 'Anthony Hopkins, Olivia Colman, Mark Gatiss, Olivia Williams, Imogen Poots'),
(138, 996, 8.1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rVNYZZgfhwqVMMWlBmxOfWqnwCj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/u546kDNwrZ1ii6q8NqqQgHwRvoW.jpg', 'en', 'Double Indemnity', 'Crime', 'Thriller', NULL, 'A rich woman and a calculating insurance agent plot to kill her unsuspecting husband after he signs a double indemnity policy. Against a backdrop of distinctly Californian settings, the partners in crime plan the perfect murder to collect the insurance, which pays double if the death is accidental.', '1944-07-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9oxVkwB05rU', 'Billy Wilder', 'Fred MacMurray, Barbara Stanwyck, Edward G. Robinson, Porter Hall, Richard Gaines'),
(139, 935, 8.123, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7SixLzxcqezkZEYU8pcHZgbkmjp.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sTp8K0SfcC2RQef1Tu160z3niHO.jpg', 'en', 'Dr. Strangelove or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb', 'Comedy', 'War', NULL, 'After the insane General Jack D. Ripper initiates a nuclear strike on the Soviet Union, a war room full of politicians, generals and a Russian diplomat all frantically try to stop the nuclear strike.', '1964-01-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ja3n2Mxf21s', 'Stanley Kubrick', 'Peter Sellers, George C. Scott, Sterling Hayden, Keenan Wynn, Slim Pickens'),
(140, 762975, 8.1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4JyNWkryifWbWXJyxcWh3pVya6N.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iQlJyRecJeGGzQGT2rEcyAgz89F.jpg', 'en', 'Purple Hearts', 'Romance', 'Drama', NULL, 'An aspiring musician agrees to a marriage of convenience with a soon-to-deploy Marine, but a tragedy soon turns their fake relationship all too real.', '2022-07-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WTLgg8oRSBE', 'Elizabeth Allen Rosenbaum', 'Sofia Carson, Nicholas Galitzine, John Harlan Kim, Chosen Jacobs, Anthony Ippolito'),
(141, 100, 8.122, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wt2TRBmFmBn5M5MBcPTwovlREaB.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cXQH2u7wUIX1eoIdEj51kHXoWhX.jpg', 'en', 'Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels', 'Comedy', 'Crime', NULL, 'A card shark and his unwillingly-enlisted friends need to make a lot of cash quick after losing a sketchy poker match. To do this they decide to pull a heist on a small-time gang who happen to be operating out of the flat next door.', '1998-08-28', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HY7mRdQuUSw', 'Guy Ritchie', 'Vinnie Jones, Jason Flemyng, Dexter Fletcher, Nick Moran, Jason Statham'),
(142, 280, 8.115, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5M0j0B18abtBI5gi2RhfjjurTqb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vINgGecnz95iDL6fjQMARDsocgG.jpg', 'en', 'Terminator 2: Judgment Day', 'Action', 'Thriller', 'Science Fiction', 'Set ten years after the events of the original, James Cameron’s classic sci-fi action flick tells the story of a second attempt to get the rid of rebellion leader John Connor, this time targeting the boy himself. However, the rebellion has sent a reprogrammed terminator to protect Connor.', '1991-07-03', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DX1Y8e7i6cw', 'James Cameron', 'Arnold Schwarzenegger, Edward Furlong, Linda Hamilton, Robert Patrick, Joe Morton'),
(143, 411088, 8.115, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fptnZJbLzKUHeNlYrAynbyoL5YJ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2Ci7ffA51O2Kub3aW4nztZIERlg.jpg', 'es', 'The Invisible Guest', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'Thriller', 'Barcelona, Spain. Adrián Doria, a young and successful businessman accused of murder, meets one night with Virginia Goodman, an expert interrogation lawyer, in order to devise a defense strategy.', '2017-01-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=epCg2RbyF80', 'Oriol Paulo', 'Mario Casas, Ana Wagener, Jose Coronado, Bárbara Lennie, Francesc Orella'),
(144, 843, 8.11, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iYypPT4bhqXfq1b6EnmxvRt6b2Y.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gx3Iat10dc39XbDwbmdfKPsow3U.jpg', 'cn', 'In the Mood for Love', 'Drama', 'Romance', NULL, 'In Hong Kong of 1962, Mrs. Chan and Mr. Chow, a journalist, move into neighbouring apartments on the same day. Their encounters are formal and polite—until a discovery about their respective spouses creates an intimate bond between them.', '2000-09-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m8GuedsQnWQ', 'Wong Kar-wai', 'Tony Leung Chiu-wai, Maggie Cheung, Rebecca Pan, Kelly Lai Chen, Siu Ping-lam'),
(145, 755812, 8.105, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9YbyvcrHmY2SVbdfXpb8mC4Fy0g.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2BZ7PC9aISswNXV2tugmjGiriaB.jpg', 'fr', 'Miraculous World: New York, United HeroeZ', 'Animation', 'TV Movie', 'Fantasy', 'Marinette’s class is headed to New York, the city of superheroes, for French-American Friendship Week. The whole class is there...except Adrien, whose father refuses to let him go!', '2020-09-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=952fktHweJs', 'Thomas Astruc', 'Annouck Hautbois, Benjamin Bollen, Antoine Tomé, Fanny Bloc, Thierry Kazazian'),
(146, 664767, 8.1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4VlXER3FImHeFuUjBShFamhIp9M.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vw3zNfzvnVNF7nIjpiEgcdznfeC.jpg', 'en', 'Mortal Kombat Legends: Scorpion\'s Revenge', 'Animation', 'Action', 'Fantasy', 'After the vicious slaughter of his family by stone-cold mercenary Sub-Zero, Hanzo Hasashi is exiled to the torturous Netherrealm. There, in exchange for his servitude to the sinister Quan Chi, he’s given a chance to avenge his family – and is resurrected as Scorpion, a lost soul bent on revenge. Back on Earthrealm, Lord Raiden gathers a team of elite warriors – Shaolin monk Liu Kang, Special Forces officer Sonya Blade and action star Johnny Cage – an unlikely band of heroes with one chance to save humanity. To do this, they must defeat Shang Tsung’s horde of Outworld gladiators and reign over the Mortal Kombat tournament.', '2020-04-12', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P87QXvvav7Y', 'Ethan Spaulding', 'Patrick Seitz, Jordan Rodrigues, Jennifer Carpenter, Joel McHale, Ike Amadi'),
(147, 555604, 8.108, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vx1u0uwxdlhV2MUzj4VlcMB0N6m.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/e782pDRAlu4BG0ahd777n8zfPzZ.jpg', 'en', 'Guillermo del Toro\'s Pinocchio', 'Animation', 'Fantasy', 'Drama', 'During the rise of fascism in Mussolini\'s Italy, a wooden boy brought magically to life struggles to live up to his father\'s expectations.', '2022-10-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Od2NW1sfRdA', 'Guillermo del Toro, Mark Gustafson', 'Ewan McGregor, David Bradley, Gregory Mann, Burn Gorman, Ron Perlman'),
(148, 46738, 8.1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/i5GsLIII66LubmOai65cWiB4kZq.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/aFmoJntgDPR0Jd8XD1ZfFSmcqMg.jpg', 'fr', 'Incendies', 'Drama', 'War', 'Mystery', 'A mother\'s last wishes send twins Jeanne and Simon on a journey to Middle East in search of their tangled roots. Adapted from Wajdi Mouawad\'s acclaimed play, Incendies tells the powerful and moving tale of two young adults\' voyage to the core of deep-rooted hatred, never-ending wars and enduring love.', '2010-09-17', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XJ69WnwvZhE', 'Denis Villeneuve', 'Lubna Azabal, Mélissa Désormeaux-Poulin, Maxim Gaudette, Rémy Girard, Allen Altman'),
(149, 655, 8.105, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tgw3TJTWgNUYCgL5Pa546VVVvSU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/moTOuNKnM2phZCYPF49Y1Hb7WJj.jpg', 'en', 'Paris, Texas', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'A man wanders out of the desert not knowing who he is. His brother finds him, and helps to pull his memory back of the life he led before he walked out on his family and disappeared four years earlier.', '1984-07-16', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nb987ysh9l8', 'Wim Wenders', 'Harry Dean Stanton, Nastassja Kinski, Dean Stockwell, Hunter Carson, Aurore Clément'),
(150, 11878, 8.1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tN7kYPjRhDolpui9sc9Eq9n5b2O.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zd7mu6dJKxkVtBdXqlEQ9W3msKl.jpg', 'ja', 'Yojimbo', 'Drama', 'Thriller', NULL, 'A nameless ronin, or samurai with no master, enters a small village in feudal Japan where two rival businessmen are struggling for control of the local gambling trade. Taking the name Sanjuro Kuwabatake, the ronin convinces both silk merchant Tazaemon and sake merchant Tokuemon to hire him as a personal bodyguard, then artfully sets in motion a full-scale gang war between the two ambitious and unscrupulous men.', '1961-04-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nazk6Zpm_Ks', 'Akira Kurosawa', 'Toshirō Mifune, Tatsuya Nakadai, Yōko Tsukasa, Isuzu Yamada, Daisuke Katō');
INSERT INTO `movies_list` (`id`, `movie_DB_Id`, `vote_average`, `poster_path`, `backdrop_path`, `original_language`, `title`, `genre_1`, `genre_2`, `genre_3`, `overview`, `release_date`, `trailer_link`, `producers`, `actors`) VALUES
(151, 705, 8.103, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/6numIZH6uR3NlJgY9m7nGH0jhs.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9ygnsnkiRp7a97KUGx9nIUjZG5P.jpg', 'en', 'All About Eve', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'From the moment she glimpses her idol at the stage door, Eve Harrington is determined to take the reins of power away from the great actress Margo Channing. Eve maneuvers her way into Margo\'s Broadway role, becomes a sensation and even causes turmoil in the lives of Margo\'s director boyfriend, her playwright and his wife. Only the cynical drama critic sees through Eve, admiring her audacity and perfect pattern of deceit.', '1950-11-09', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ktG-ilbXbtI', 'Joseph L. Mankiewicz', 'Bette Davis, Anne Baxter, George Sanders, Celeste Holm, Gary Merrill'),
(152, 103663, 8.101, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jkixsXzRh28q3PCqFoWcf7unghT.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7zN7m5jEyrNxFYm2EbQJAZwAG5i.jpg', 'da', 'The Hunt', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'A teacher lives a lonely life, all the while struggling over his son’s custody. His life slowly gets better as he finds love and receives good news from his son, but his new luck is about to be brutally shattered by an innocent little lie.', '2012-06-13', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0KwzEQPMppI', 'Thomas Vinterberg', 'Mads Mikkelsen, Thomas Bo Larsen, Annika Wedderkopp, Lasse Fogelstrøm, Susse Wold'),
(153, 239, 8.101, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hVIKyTK13AvOGv7ICmJjK44DTzp.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5zTwAcnI3zCJ0mucPPnoBtkSWEV.jpg', 'en', 'Some Like It Hot', 'Comedy', 'Romance', 'Crime', 'Two musicians witness a mob hit and struggle to find a way out of the city before they are found by the gangsters. Their only opportunity is to join an all-girl band as they leave on a tour. To make their getaway they must first disguise themselves as women, then keep their identities secret and deal with the problems this brings - such as an attractive bandmate and a very determined suitor.', '1959-03-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=97TYs2YXbJw', 'Billy Wilder', 'Tony Curtis, Jack Lemmon, Marilyn Monroe, George Raft, Pat O’Brien'),
(154, 38, 8.101, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5MwkWH9tYHv3mV9OdYTMR5qreIz.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/12imOn96zRI2EMHOjOxm2qNY2BA.jpg', 'en', 'Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind', 'Science Fiction', 'Drama', 'Romance', 'Joel Barish, heartbroken that his girlfriend underwent a procedure to erase him from her memory, decides to do the same. However, as he watches his memories of her fade away, he realises that he still loves her, and may be too late to correct his mistake.', '2004-03-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yE-f1alkq9I', 'Michel Gondry', 'Jim Carrey, Kate Winslet, Kirsten Dunst, Mark Ruffalo, Elijah Wood'),
(155, 146233, 8.098, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uhviyknTT5cEQXbn6vWIqfM4vGm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3RFmTz5h2UuFWEV4oH00XICBR9y.jpg', 'en', 'Prisoners', 'Drama', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'Keller Dover is facing every parent’s worst nightmare. His six-year-old daughter, Anna, is missing, together with her young friend, Joy, and as minutes turn to hours, panic sets in. The only lead is a dilapidated RV that had earlier been parked on their street.', '2013-09-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=doPNgss-ntc', 'Denis Villeneuve', 'Hugh Jackman, Jake Gyllenhaal, Viola Davis, Maria Bello, Terrence Howard'),
(156, 9702, 8.1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gvP6R6juhe2IpCG7QGDgjyUvm0g.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9xjUZjuYyehv2qnqMH0oR9nSTft.jpg', 'en', 'Bound by Honor', 'Crime', 'Action', 'Drama', 'Based on the true life experiences of poet Jimmy Santiago Baca, the film focuses on half-brothers Paco and Cruz, and their bi-racial cousin Miklo. It opens in 1972, as the three are members of an East L.A. gang known as the \"Vatos Locos\", and the story focuses on how a violent crime and the influence of narcotics alter their lives. Miklo is incarcerated and sent to San Quentin, where he makes a \"home\" for himself. Cruz becomes an exceptional artist, but a heroin addiction overcomes him with tragic results. Paco becomes a cop and an enemy to his \"carnal\", Miklo.', '1993-02-05', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NMj89zgI8Yc', 'Taylor Hackford', 'Damian Chapa, Jesse Borrego, Benjamin Bratt, Enrique Castillo, Victor Rivers'),
(157, 12445, 8.097, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/c54HpQmuwXjHq2C9wmoACjxoom3.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/n5A7brJCjejceZmHyujwUTVgQNC.jpg', 'en', 'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2', 'Fantasy', 'Adventure', NULL, 'Harry, Ron and Hermione continue their quest to vanquish the evil Voldemort once and for all. Just as things begin to look hopeless for the young wizards, Harry discovers a trio of magical objects that endow him with powers to rival Voldemort\'s formidable skills.', '2011-07-12', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5NYt1qirBWg', 'David Yates', 'Daniel Radcliffe, Emma Watson, Rupert Grint, Ralph Fiennes, Alan Rickman'),
(158, 439, 8.096, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2KU52apQyvyZuPsqEGMcWb4BKu2.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zPbu0CFnAT2kYfbGWjgZBTajmzi.jpg', 'it', 'La Dolce Vita', 'Comedy', 'Drama', NULL, 'Episodic journey of journalist Marcello who struggles to find his place in the world, torn between the allure of Rome\'s elite social scene and the stifling domesticity offered by his girlfriend, all the while searching for a way to become a serious writer.', '1960-02-05', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1BeWEPXWDX4', 'Federico Fellini', 'Marcello Mastroianni, Anita Ekberg, Anouk Aimée, Yvonne Furneaux, Magali Noël'),
(159, 406, 8.096, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8rgPyWjYZhsphSSxbXguMnhN7H0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/viGCwLxupyoaLsa6hrnu1gYrB0B.jpg', 'fr', 'La Haine', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'After a chaotic night of rioting in a marginal suburb of Paris, three young friends, Vinz, Hubert and Saïd, wander around unoccupied waiting for news about the state of health of a mutual friend who has been seriously injured when confronting the police.', '1995-05-31', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MjEVNWNhA1o', 'Mathieu Kassovitz', 'Vincent Cassel, Hubert Koundé, Saïd Taghmaoui, Abdel Ahmed Ghili, Solo'),
(160, 397567, 8.094, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gJSvIsI6oQfFim0PGyuuiCYfqKs.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/inaX9PA89bJg0jE8TtEpdOX5R8D.jpg', 'ko', 'Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds', 'Action', 'Adventure', 'Drama', 'Having died unexpectedly, firefighter Ja-hong is taken to the afterlife by 3 afterlife guardians. Only when he passes 7 trials over 49 days and proves he was innocent in human life, he’s able to reincarnate, and his 3 afterlife guardians are by his side to defend him in trial.', '2017-12-20', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dyh_OY1DgqU', 'Kim Yong-hwa', 'Ha Jung-woo, Cha Tae-hyun, Ju Ji-hoon, Kim Hyang-gi, Lee Jung-jae'),
(161, 872585, 8.094, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nb3xI8XI3w4pMVZ38VijbsyBqP4.jpg', 'en', 'Oppenheimer', 'Drama', 'History', NULL, 'The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer\'s role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.', '2023-07-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qiuSBWVdgLI', 'Christopher Nolan', 'Cillian Murphy, Emily Blunt, Matt Damon, Robert Downey Jr., Florence Pugh'),
(162, 10681, 8.092, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hbhFnRzzg6ZDmm8YAmxBnQpQIPh.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fK5ssgvtI43z19FoWigdlqgpLRE.jpg', 'en', 'WALL·E', 'Animation', 'Family', 'Science Fiction', 'In the distant future, Earth has become a desolate wasteland, abandoned by humanity and overrun by mountains of trash. Amidst the rubble, a small, lovable robot named WALL-E spends his days tirelessly cleaning up the mess. But when a sleek, high-tech robot named EVE arrives on a mission to search for signs of life, WALL-E is immediately smitten. Together, they embark on a journey across the cosmos.', '2008-06-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tbr_L9Gap_M', 'Andrew Stanton', 'Elissa Knight, Jeff Garlin, Fred Willard, John Ratzenberger, Kathy Najimy'),
