(197, 337404, 8.015, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wToO8opxkGwKgSfJ1JK8tGvkG6U.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/6MKr3KgOLmzOP6MSuZERO41Lpkt.jpg', 'en', 'Cruella', 'Comedy', 'Crime', NULL, 'In 1970s London amidst the punk rock revolution, a young grifter named Estella is determined to make a name for herself with her designs. She befriends a pair of young thieves who appreciate her appetite for mischief, and together they are able to build a life for themselves on the London streets. One day, Estella’s flair for fashion catches the eye of the Baroness von Hellman, a fashion legend who is devastatingly chic and terrifyingly haute. But their relationship sets in motion a course of events and revelations that will cause Estella to embrace her wicked side and become the raucous, fashionable and revenge-bent Cruella.', '2021-05-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jpZrVxvG3mk', 'Craig Gillespie', 'Emma Stone, Emma Thompson, Joel Fry, Paul Walter Hauser, John McCrea'),
(198, 678512, 8.013, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kSf9svfL2WrKeuK8W08xeR5lTn8.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/P3GAbRjzVo9RKU4WxzvtgwlITc.jpg', 'en', 'Sound of Freedom', 'Action', 'Drama', NULL, 'The story of Tim Ballard, a former US government agent, who quits his job in order to devote his life to rescuing children from global sex traffickers.', '2023-07-03', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rt0kp4VW1cI', 'Alejandro Monteverde', 'Jim Caviezel, Mira Sorvino, Bill Camp, Gerardo Taracena, Kurt Fuller'),
(199, 11778, 8.012, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/bbGtogDZOg09bm42KIpCXUXICkh.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/a5zBQfXmLk3qqRYF7AioWpiAxk2.jpg', 'en', 'The Deer Hunter', 'Drama', 'War', NULL, 'A group of working-class friends decide to enlist in the Army during the Vietnam War and finds it to be hellish chaos -- not the noble venture they imagined. Before they left, Steven married his pregnant girlfriend -- and Michael and Nick were in love with the same woman. But all three are different men upon their return.', '1978-12-08', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g7q1SjVdsNk', 'Michael Cimino', 'Robert De Niro, Christopher Walken, John Cazale, John Savage, Meryl Streep'),
(200, 3175, 8.011, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dOJtBSyI30wWc08UmyEKLsu4Rfk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7ZT8AdGAzK7hv8JhQ0tCtEZ72JP.jpg', 'en', 'Barry Lyndon', 'Drama', 'Romance', 'War', 'An Irish rogue uses his cunning and wit to work his way up the social classes of 18th century England, transforming himself from the humble Redmond Barry into the noble Barry Lyndon.', '1975-12-18', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XjPSGuJskxM', 'Stanley Kubrick', 'Ryan O\'Neal, Marisa Berenson, Patrick Magee, Hardy Krüger, Steven Berkoff'),
(201, 15, 8.011, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sav0jxhqiH0bPr2vZFU0Kjt2nZL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ruF3Lmd4A8MHbnEBE6lxPMbsHGL.jpg', 'en', 'Citizen Kane', 'Mystery', 'Drama', NULL, 'Newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane is taken from his mother as a boy and made the ward of a rich industrialist. As a result, every well-meaning, tyrannical or self-destructive move he makes for the rest of his life appears in some way to be a reaction to that deeply wounding event.', '1941-04-17', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fAcLNMkzfTE', 'Orson Welles', 'Joseph Cotten, Dorothy Comingore, Ray Collins, George Coulouris, Agnes Moorehead'),
(202, 110416, 8.01, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3DBX7QOEzWPNcDhqXInk6GBEvhK.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/AaIRBsx4hpa2fVQzeCfFyOdzCEM.jpg', 'en', 'Song of the Sea', 'Family', 'Animation', 'Fantasy', 'The story of the last Seal Child’s journey home. After their mother’s disappearance, Ben and Saoirse are sent to live with Granny in the city. When they resolve to return to their home by the sea, their journey becomes a race against time as they are drawn into a world Ben knows only from his mother’s folktales. But this is no bedtime story; these fairy folk have been in our world far too long. It soon becomes clear to Ben that Saoirse is the key to their survival.', '2014-06-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VrhoOzW8oF8', 'Tomm Moore', 'David Rawle, Lucy O\'Connell, Brendan Gleeson, Fionnula Flanagan, Pat Shortt'),
(203, 449176, 8.009, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5YUYg5q7QfC4IoNwNUtiwdiYKPr.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/oYGdeZrrmEUaORDz2NPi5sYWaKn.jpg', 'en', 'Love, Simon', 'Comedy', 'Drama', 'Romance', 'Everyone deserves a great love story, but for 17-year-old Simon Spier, it\'s a little more complicated. He hasn\'t told his family or friends that he\'s gay, and he doesn\'t know the identity of the anonymous classmate that he\'s fallen for online.', '2018-02-16', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E0cbWdlQg_8', 'Greg Berlanti', 'Nick Robinson, Jennifer Garner, Josh Duhamel, Katherine Langford, Alexandra Shipp'),
(204, 43949, 8.009, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/6zDYFigohwncqFL00MKbFV01dWb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xBSwwkAYl9h8QVG2OxNpSaSgJwr.jpg', 'en', 'Flipped', 'Romance', 'Drama', NULL, 'When Juli meets Bryce in the second grade, she knows it\'s true love. After spending six years trying to convince Bryce the same, she\'s ready to give up - until he starts to reconsider.', '2010-08-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aXeJ8NM7c9g', 'Rob Reiner', 'Madeline Carroll, Callan McAuliffe, Rebecca De Mornay, Anthony Edwards, John Mahoney'),
(205, 524, 8.008, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4TS5O1IP42bY2BvgMxL156EENy.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iZGiMD0p1M2AOmzKknFo5bkuz94.jpg', 'en', 'Casino', 'Crime', 'Drama', NULL, 'In early-1970s Las Vegas, Sam \"Ace\" Rothstein gets tapped by his bosses to head the Tangiers Casino. At first, he\'s a great success in the job, but over the years, problems with his loose-cannon enforcer Nicky Santoro, his ex-hustler wife Ginger, her con-artist ex Lester Diamond and a handful of corrupt politicians put Sam in ever-increasing danger.', '1995-11-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AIRRDirf4KY', 'Martin Scorsese', 'Robert De Niro, Sharon Stone, Joe Pesci, James Woods, Don Rickles'),
(206, 28178, 8.007, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/lsy3aEsEfYIHdLRk4dontZ4s85h.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/y6JA85N8DvoonwqDGWlgkr1jnU.jpg', 'en', 'Hachi: A Dog\'s Tale', 'Drama', 'Family', NULL, 'A drama based on the true story of a college professor\'s bond with the abandoned dog he takes into his home.', '2009-06-08', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6U7mAnPtw4', 'Lasse Hallström', 'Richard Gere, Joan Allen, Sarah Roemer, Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa, Erick Avari'),
(207, 947, 8.008, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/AiAm0EtDvyGqNpVoieRw4u65vD1.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/6wmemKdbkOIaWfzz607K21R6qOh.jpg', 'en', 'Lawrence of Arabia', 'Adventure', 'History', 'War', 'The story of British officer T.E. Lawrence\'s mission to aid the Arab tribes in their revolt against the Ottoman Empire during the First World War. Lawrence becomes a flamboyant, messianic figure in the cause of Arab unity but his psychological instability threatens to undermine his achievements.', '1962-12-11', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KR1yTI8zFJk', 'David Lean', 'Peter O\'Toole, Alec Guinness, Anthony Quinn, Jack Hawkins, Omar Sharif'),
(208, 595, 8.006, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gZycFUMLx2110dzK3nBNai7gfpM.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hYZICJYYKBqlmm1YBN483YbTN5j.jpg', 'en', 'To Kill a Mockingbird', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Scout Finch, 6, and her older brother Jem live in sleepy Maycomb, Alabama, spending much of their time with their friend Dill and spying on their reclusive and mysterious neighbor, Boo Radley. When Atticus, their widowed father and a respected lawyer, defends a black man named Tom Robinson against fabricated rape charges, the trial and tangent events expose the children to evils of racism and stereotyping.', '1962-12-20', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4-CrrtYjrbM', 'Robert Mulligan', 'Mary Badham, Gregory Peck, Phillip Alford, John Megna, Frank Overton'),
(209, 568160, 8.005, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/qgrk7r1fV4IjuoeiGS5HOhXNdLJ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wRDyTXw5j0RN9M03xZlHYkoNLCI.jpg', 'ja', 'Weathering with You', 'Animation', 'Drama', 'Fantasy', 'The summer of his high school freshman year, Hodaka runs away from his remote island home to Tokyo, and quickly finds himself pushed to his financial and personal limits. The weather is unusually gloomy and rainy every day, as if taking its cue from his life. After many days of solitude, he finally finds work as a freelance writer for a mysterious occult magazine. Then, one day, Hodaka meets Hina on a busy street corner. This bright and strong-willed girl possesses a strange and wonderful ability: the power to stop the rain and clear the sky.', '2019-06-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q6iK6DjV_iE', 'Makoto Shinkai', 'Kotaro Daigo, Nana Mori, Tsubasa Honda, Sakura Kiryu, Sei Hiraizumi'),
(210, 359724, 8.005, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dR1Ju50iudrOh3YgfwkAU1g2HZe.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2vq5GTJOahE03mNYZGxIynlHcWr.jpg', 'en', 'Ford v Ferrari', 'Drama', 'Action', 'History', 'American car designer Carroll Shelby and the British-born driver Ken Miles work together to battle corporate interference, the laws of physics, and their own personal demons to build a revolutionary race car for Ford Motor Company and take on the dominating race cars of Enzo Ferrari at the 24 Hours of Le Mans in France in 1966.', '2019-11-13', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I3h9Z89U9ZA', 'James Mangold', 'Matt Damon, Christian Bale, Jon Bernthal, Caitríona Balfe, Josh Lucas'),
(211, 339877, 8.005, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/56sq57kDm7XgyXBYrgJLumo0Jac.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xW54kLO7ZB683CwMbGSN3ELSS1K.jpg', 'en', 'Loving Vincent', 'Animation', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'A young man arrives at the last hometown of painter Vincent van Gogh to deliver the troubled artist\'s final letter and ends up investigating his final days there.', '2017-06-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gy0RVDM1sNA', 'DK Welchman, Hugh Welchman', 'Douglas Booth, Robert Gulaczyk, Eleanor Tomlinson, Helen McCrory, Saoirse Ronan'),
(212, 962, 8.005, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/eQRFo1qwRREYwj47Yoe1PisgOle.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hZHeDPQGNKN9NN9GuW7qVbM2tDx.jpg', 'en', 'The Gold Rush', 'Adventure', 'Comedy', 'Drama', 'A gold prospector in Alaska struggles to survive the elements and win the heart of a dance hall girl.', '1925-07-12', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cSSZiPHkXio', 'Charlie Chaplin', 'Charlie Chaplin, Georgia Hale, Mack Swain, Tom Murray, Henry Bergman'),
(213, 205596, 8.002, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zSqJ1qFq8NXFfi7JeIYMlzyR0dx.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gLQoJ9P79g501oEEtrN8zMlCPpx.jpg', 'en', 'The Imitation Game', 'History', 'Drama', 'Thriller', 'Based on the real life story of legendary cryptanalyst Alan Turing, the film portrays the nail-biting race against time by Turing and his brilliant team of code-breakers at Britain\'s top-secret Government Code and Cypher School at Bletchley Park, during the darkest days of World War II.', '2014-11-14', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j2jRs4EAvWM', 'Morten Tyldum', 'Benedict Cumberbatch, Keira Knightley, Matthew Goode, Rory Kinnear, Allen Leech'),
(214, 140420, 8.002, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/6MXYNvGmI63W8fI3HKlcZzEy1U5.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uXXvFU16v3cH8gIUWx3WCbAt29a.jpg', 'en', 'Paperman', 'Animation', 'Family', 'Romance', 'An urban office worker finds that paper airplanes are instrumental in meeting a girl in ways he never expected.', '2012-11-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mM6cLnscmO8', 'John Kahrs', 'Kari Wahlgren, Jack Goldenberg'),
(215, 25376, 8.002, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dkeAwfZzwL3WvToydE3CXiY80E0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fNHCogWhABNAmzk0IFdzQP5XLYj.jpg', 'es', 'The Secret in Their Eyes', 'Mystery', 'Thriller', 'Drama', 'Hoping to put to rest years of unease concerning a past case, retired criminal investigator Benjamín begins writing a novel based on the unsolved mystery of a newlywed’s rape and murder. With the help of a former colleague, judge Irene, he attempts to make sense of the past.', '2009-08-13', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZhEuUDO0YUQ', 'Juan José Campanella', 'Ricardo Darín, Soledad Villamil, Pablo Rago, Javier Godino, Guillermo Francella'),
(216, 530915, 7.994, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iZf0KyrE25z1sage4SYFLCCrMi9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/76LpPdXtCf4WxWDagVT2YcF4e9g.jpg', 'en', '1917', 'War', 'Action', 'Drama', 'At the height of the First World War, two young British soldiers must cross enemy territory and deliver a message that will stop a deadly attack on hundreds of soldiers.', '2019-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gZjQROMAh_s', 'Sam Mendes', 'George MacKay, Dean-Charles Chapman, Mark Strong, Andrew Scott, Richard Madden'),
(217, 20453, 7.993, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/66A9MqXOyVFCssoloscw79z8Tew.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/u7kuUaySqXBVAtqEl9vkTkAzHV9.jpg', 'hi', '3 Idiots', 'Drama', 'Comedy', NULL, 'Rascal. Joker. Dreamer. Genius... You\'ve never met a college student quite like \"Rancho.\" From the moment he arrives at India\'s most prestigious university, Rancho\'s outlandish schemes turn the campus upside down—along with the lives of his two newfound best friends. Together, they make life miserable for \"Virus,\" the school’s uptight and heartless dean. But when Rancho catches the eye of the dean\'s daughter, Virus sets his sights on flunking out the \"3 idiots\" once and for all.', '2009-12-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K0eDlFX9GMc', 'Rajkumar Hirani', 'Aamir Khan, R. Madhavan, Sharman Joshi, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Boman Irani'),
(218, 13223, 7.992, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zUybYvxWdAJy5hhYovsXtHSWI1l.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wmsePXV2z1b6ecXuKKrFbG0Q92P.jpg', 'en', 'Gran Torino', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Disgruntled Korean War veteran Walt Kowalski sets out to reform his neighbor, Thao Lor, a Hmong teenager who tried to steal Kowalski\'s prized possession: a 1972 Gran Torino.', '2008-12-12', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F8zue_BzNsw', 'Clint Eastwood', 'Clint Eastwood, Christopher Carley, Bee Vang, Ahney Her, Brian Haley'),
(219, 11104, 7.988, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/43I9DcNoCzpyzK8JCkJYpHqHqGG.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/u76U7t1v5pulSr8XOEZ4W41xN1x.jpg', 'cn', 'Chungking Express', 'Drama', 'Comedy', 'Romance', 'Two melancholic Hong Kong policemen fall in love: one with a mysterious underworld figure, the other with a beautiful and ethereal server at a late-night restaurant.', '1994-07-14', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P9Mxf_6pVA0', 'Wong Kar-wai', 'Takeshi Kaneshiro, Brigitte Lin, Tony Leung Chiu-wai, Faye Wong, Valerie Chow'),
(220, 7508, 7.988, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fwXhw9bERqKrJfJK6WGakPIh3FS.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/bPwdy3zaNnMdZ22u0WCcYu0xxgt.jpg', 'hi', 'Like Stars on Earth', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Ishaan Awasthi is an eight-year-old whose world is filled with wonders that no one else seems to appreciate. Colours, fish, dogs, and kites don\'t seem important to the adults, who are much more interested in things like homework, marks, and neatness. Ishaan cannot seem to get anything right in class; he is then sent to boarding school, where his life changes forever.', '2007-12-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tn_2Ie_jtX8', 'Aamir Khan', 'Darsheel Safary, Tisca Chopra, Vipin Sharma, Aamir Khan, Tanay Chheda'),
(221, 930094, 7.987, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dD3vhyDRCCT90hf4rldHU6Wu3Va.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/csz3oWxd04wgXUzenXgenIVwXGl.jpg', 'en', 'Red, White & Royal Blue', 'Comedy', 'Romance', NULL, 'After an altercation between Alex, the president\'s son, and Britain\'s Prince Henry at a royal event becomes tabloid fodder, their long-running feud now threatens to drive a wedge in U.S./British relations. When the rivals are forced into a staged truce, their icy relationship begins to thaw and the friction between them sparks something deeper than they ever expected.', '2023-07-27', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pt56IC8gDZ4', 'Matthew López', 'Taylor Zakhar Perez, Nicholas Galitzine, Uma Thurman, Clifton Collins Jr., Rachel Hilson'),
(222, 424694, 7.986, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/lHu1wtNaczFPGFDTrjCSzeLPTKN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xcaSYLBhmDzJ6P14bcKe0KTh3QV.jpg', 'en', 'Bohemian Rhapsody', 'Music', 'Drama', NULL, 'Singer Freddie Mercury, guitarist Brian May, drummer Roger Taylor and bass guitarist John Deacon take the music world by storm when they form the rock \'n\' roll band Queen in 1970. Hit songs become instant classics. When Mercury\'s increasingly wild lifestyle starts to spiral out of control, Queen soon faces its greatest challenge yet – finding a way to keep the band together amid the success and excess.', '2018-10-24', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=27zlBpzdOZg', 'Bryan Singer', 'Rami Malek, Gwilym Lee, Ben Hardy, Joseph Mazzello, Lucy Boynton'),
(223, 488623, 7.987, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cBgj41y1RvmW1zJCEX0uNWL0UjW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wb1hz8m3snCBN1wdF3SZxrdKgRH.jpg', 'ko', 'Forgotten', 'Thriller', 'Mystery', 'Crime', 'Seoul, South Korea, 1997. When the young but extremely anxious student Jin-seok, his parents and his successful older brother Yoo-seok move to a new home, mysterious and frightening events begin to happen around them, unexplained events that threaten to ruin their seemingly happy lives. Unable to understand what is happening, Jin-seok wonders if he is losing his mind.', '2017-11-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5fAD6PqBMQ', 'Jang Hang-jun', 'Kang Ha-neul, Kim Moo-yul, Moon Sung-keun, Na Young-hee, Nam Myung-ryeol'),
(224, 3090, 7.984, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pWcst7zVbi8Z8W6GFrdNE7HHRxL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sj5R5SGor3YMFBuabMj8gPbyBmh.jpg', 'en', 'The Treasure of the Sierra Madre', 'Adventure', 'Drama', 'Western', 'Fred C. Dobbs and Bob Curtin, both down on their luck in Tampico, Mexico in 1925, meet up with a grizzled prospector named Howard and decide to join with him in search of gold in the wilds of central Mexico. Through enormous difficulties, they eventually succeed in finding gold, but bandits, the elements, and most especially greed threaten to turn their success into disaster.', '1948-01-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XZ8Q9mOYJgE', 'John Huston', 'Humphrey Bogart, Walter Huston, Tim Holt, Bruce Bennett, Barton MacLane'),
(225, 213, 8, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ay0dOKJgyK4VEh3xakV15UgvJMF.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/OR8oloCZ3klJtB7Y0i8pSqWw5a.jpg', 'en', 'North by Northwest', 'Mystery', 'Thriller', 'Adventure', 'Advertising man Roger Thornhill is mistaken for a spy, triggering a deadly cross-country chase.', '1959-07-08', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P6ftFG7xC4M', 'Alfred Hitchcock', 'Cary Grant, Eva Marie Saint, James Mason, Jessie Royce Landis, Leo G. Carroll'),
(226, 10515, 7.982, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/41XxSsJc5OrulP0m7TrrUeO2hoz.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3cyjYtLWCBE1uvWINHFsFnE8LUK.jpg', 'ja', 'Castle in the Sky', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', 'Animation', 'A young boy and a girl with a magic crystal must race against pirates and foreign agents in a search for a legendary floating castle.', '1986-08-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6s_wR3uuWec', 'Hayao Miyazaki', 'Keiko Yokozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Minori Terada, Kotoe Hatsui, Fujio Tokita');
