(424, 11005, 7.766, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9gztZXuHLG6AJ0fgqGd7Q43cWRI.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zP7DP2AmOCTgUa0nOMA2TLAjKqz.jpg', 'en', 'Awakenings', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Dr. Malcolm Sayer, a shy research physician, uses an experimental drug to \"awaken\" the catatonic victims of a rare disease. Leonard is the first patient to receive the controversial treatment. His awakening, filled with awe and enthusiasm, proves a rebirth for Sayer too, as the exuberant patient reveals life\'s simple but unutterably sweet pleasures to the introverted doctor.', '1990-12-04', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7exeVt7CaE4', 'Penny Marshall', 'Robert De Niro, Robin Williams, John Heard, Julie Kavner, Penelope Ann Miller'),
(425, 117, 7.766, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jB8ROzQOr3p4ygSzyPjLhUqCOFu.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/i1oWUGVDNBhGBykcCRBlX326udb.jpg', 'en', 'The Untouchables', 'Crime', 'History', 'Thriller', 'Elliot Ness, an ambitious prohibition agent, is determined to take down Al Capone. In order to achieve this goal, he forms a group given the nickname “The Untouchables”.', '1987-06-03', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbzkK06MJjE', 'Brian De Palma', 'Kevin Costner, Sean Connery, Charles Martin Smith, Andy García, Robert De Niro'),
(426, 336804, 7.8, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sXg3JjxCkgWw5B4VVk8lfcYImne.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nBxP0PY7yGfId9E12yo5R7x27ZQ.jpg', 'tr', 'Mustang', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'In a Turkish village, five orphaned sisters live under strict rule while members of their family prepare their arranged marriages.', '2015-06-17', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r_JXyi1EGJk', 'Deniz Gamze Ergüven', 'Güneş Nezihe Şensoy, Doğa Zeynep Doğuşlu, Elit İşcan, Tuğba Sunguroğlu, Ilayda Akdoğan'),
(427, 925, 7.763, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/63rmSDPahrH7C1gEFYzRuIBAN9W.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/leT6tupwfYea4T0zYBafP73gXj9.jpg', 'en', 'Do the Right Thing', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Salvatore \"Sal\" Fragione is the Italian owner of a pizzeria in Brooklyn. A neighborhood local, Buggin\' Out, becomes upset when he sees that the pizzeria\'s Wall of Fame exhibits only Italian actors. Buggin\' Out believes a pizzeria in a black neighborhood should showcase black actors, but Sal disagrees. The wall becomes a symbol of racism and hate to Buggin\' Out and to other people in the neighborhood, and tensions rise.', '1989-06-14', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yVAD4fYRcvA', 'Spike Lee', 'Danny Aiello, Ossie Davis, Richard Edson, John Turturro, Ruby Dee'),
(428, 380, 7.763, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iTNHwO896WKkaoPtpMMS74d8VNi.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mrfbeWcjgSaZ9NEb0xJMR9xzSeB.jpg', 'en', 'Rain Man', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'When car dealer Charlie Babbitt learns that his estranged father has died, he returns home to Cincinnati, where he discovers that he has a savant older brother named Raymond and that his father\'s $3 million fortune is being left to the mental institution in which Raymond lives. Motivated by his father\'s money, Charlie checks Raymond out of the facility in order to return with him to Los Angeles. The brothers\' cross-country trip ends up changing both their lives.', '1988-12-12', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LPyO0xBv3Gc', 'Barry Levinson', 'Tom Cruise, Dustin Hoffman, Valeria Golino, Jack Murdock, Michael D. Roberts'),
(429, 1700, 7.762, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/23Y65uWaVMpqfbZTN3CT0aei4D5.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rUAn3Ul1tL7JXMjZ951UOI3F0UA.jpg', 'en', 'Misery', 'Drama', 'Thriller', NULL, 'After stalking and saving the life of her favorite fiction author in a car accident, his  manic obsessor holds him captive in her remote Colorado home then forces him to write back to life the popular literary character he killed off.', '1990-11-30', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9HU-RfV7QA0', 'Rob Reiner', 'James Caan, Kathy Bates, Richard Farnsworth, Frances Sternhagen, Lauren Bacall'),
(430, 587, 7.762, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tjK063yCgaBAluVU72rZ6PKPH2l.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/bLqUd0tBvKezDr9MEla7k34i3rp.jpg', 'en', 'Big Fish', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', 'Drama', 'Throughout his life Edward Bloom has always been a man of big appetites, enormous passions and tall tales. In his later years, he remains a huge mystery to his son, William. Now, to get to know the real man, Will begins piecing together a true picture of his father from flashbacks of his amazing adventures.', '2003-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T6M-jwyz28U', 'Tim Burton', 'Ewan McGregor, Albert Finney, Billy Crudup, Jessica Lange, Helena Bonham Carter'),
(431, 165, 7.762, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hQq8xZe5uLjFzSBt4LanNP7SQjl.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/skQN2UMQKQnOTmwplcYMx6ZF4jS.jpg', 'en', 'Back to the Future Part II', 'Adventure', 'Comedy', 'Science Fiction', 'Marty and Doc are at it again in this wacky sequel to the 1985 blockbuster as the time-traveling duo head to 2015 to nip some McFly family woes in the bud. But things go awry thanks to bully Biff Tannen and a pesky sports almanac. In a last-ditch attempt to set things straight, Marty finds himself bound for 1955 and face to face with his teenage parents -- again.', '1989-11-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M8kvj07HpFI', 'Robert Zemeckis', 'Michael J. Fox, Christopher Lloyd, Lea Thompson, Thomas F. Wilson, Elisabeth Shue'),
(432, 6844, 7.76, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/stSpFp2NUJMGhIyndqwBi9WE9y9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rI1u4JgtnAZC99wXX4gwro4yaxe.jpg', 'en', 'The Ten Commandments', 'Drama', 'History', NULL, 'Escaping death, a Hebrew infant is raised in a royal household to become a prince. Upon discovery of his true heritage, Moses embarks on a personal quest to reclaim his destiny as the leader and liberator of the Hebrew people.', '1956-10-05', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KBzbyIPWVT4', 'Cecil B. DeMille', 'Charlton Heston, Yul Brynner, Anne Baxter, Edward G. Robinson, Yvonne De Carlo'),
(433, 937278, 7.76, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/130H1gap9lFfiTF9iDrqNIkFvC9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/v2LilmCylr3bL9TCZSj6syjowZh.jpg', 'en', 'A Man Called Otto', 'Comedy', 'Drama', NULL, 'When a lively young family moves in next door, grumpy widower Otto Anderson meets his match in a quick-witted, pregnant woman named Marisol, leading to an unlikely friendship that turns his world upside down.', '2022-12-28', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XvbGalkHKPY', 'Marc Forster', 'Tom Hanks, Mariana Treviño, Rachel Keller, John Higgins, Tony Bingham'),
(434, 579974, 7.761, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/u0XUBNQWlOvrh0Gd97ARGpIkL0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/i0Y0wP8H6SRgjr6QmuwbtQbS24D.jpg', 'te', 'RRR', 'Action', 'Drama', NULL, 'A fictional history of two legendary revolutionaries\' journey away from home before they began fighting for their country in the 1920s.', '2022-03-24', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i4pjiLGUTtk', 'S. S. Rajamouli', 'N.T. Rama Rao Jr., Ram Charan, Olivia Morris, Ray Stevenson, Alison Doody'),
(435, 303, 7.759, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yUjKnpColooH88BFQJwwgNOQ56N.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9K8MWPiEVNV1FkxiVTV0HuZvNfa.jpg', 'en', 'Notorious', 'Thriller', 'Romance', 'Mystery', 'In order to help bring Nazis to justice, U.S. government agent T.R. Devlin recruits Alicia Huberman, the American daughter of a convicted German war criminal, as a spy. As they begin to fall for one another, Alicia is instructed to win the affections of Alexander Sebastian, a Nazi hiding out in Brazil. When Sebastian becomes serious about his relationship with Alicia, the stakes get higher, and Devlin must watch her slip further undercover.', '1946-08-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EhMyp8ZvjWs', 'Alfred Hitchcock', 'Cary Grant, Ingrid Bergman, Claude Rains, Leopoldine Konstantin, Louis Calhern'),
(436, 14756, 7.758, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ggTTUXZg7trvAhsVj3eyd65bAnh.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/69QJSMkm5Hh0x9fLElZ8hjv5N4P.jpg', 'cn', 'Ip Man', 'Drama', 'Action', 'History', 'A semi-biographical account of Yip Man, the first martial arts master to teach the Chinese martial art of Wing Chun. The film focuses on events surrounding Ip that took place in the city of Foshan between the 1930s to 1940s during the Second Sino-Japanese War. Directed by Wilson Yip, the film stars Donnie Yen in the lead role, and features fight choreography by Sammo Hung.', '2008-12-12', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3IUR6P5VwGo', 'Wilson Yip', 'Donnie Yen, Simon Yam, Lynn Hung, Hiroyuki Ikeuchi, Lam Ka-tung'),
(437, 583, 7.758, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/lSSA64WF0M0BXnjwr2quMh6shCl.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/bSkJttePygyoEzUlKqKbpIokmJC.jpg', 'en', 'Life of Brian', 'Comedy', NULL, NULL, 'Brian Cohen is an average young Jewish man, but through a series of ridiculous events, he gains a reputation as the Messiah. When he\'s not dodging his followers or being scolded by his shrill mother, the hapless Brian has to contend with the pompous Pontius Pilate and acronym-obsessed members of a separatist movement. Rife with Monty Python\'s signature absurdity, the tale finds Brian\'s life paralleling Biblical lore, albeit with many more laughs.', '1979-08-17', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tK4Qb51ftd4', 'Terry Jones', 'Graham Chapman, John Cleese, Eric Idle, Terry Jones, Michael Palin'),
(438, 13855, 7.759, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hy49xJiKN1nakkN1ZmKuOf6vQYR.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/urBBFQrrVxy7T8uytrn7dOoHqZn.jpg', 'ko', 'The Chaser', 'Crime', 'Thriller', 'Action', 'Joong-ho is a dirty detective turned pimp in financial trouble as several of his girls have recently disappeared without clearing their debts. While trying to track them down, he finds a clue that the vanished girls were all called up by the same client whom one of his girls is meeting with right now.', '2008-02-14', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=akiHkFxV24w', 'Na Hong-jin', 'Kim Yoon-seok, Ha Jung-woo, Seo Young-hee, Kim You-jung, Jeong In-gi'),
(439, 317442, 7.756, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/bAQ8O5Uw6FedtlCbJTutenzPVKd.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/l8ubUlfzlB5R2j9cJ3CN7tj0gmd.jpg', 'ja', 'The Last: Naruto the Movie', 'Action', 'Romance', 'Animation', 'Two years after the events of the Fourth Great Ninja War, the moon that Hagoromo Otsutsuki created long ago to seal away the Gedo Statue begins to descend towards the world, threatening to become a meteor that would destroy everything on impact. Amidst this crisis, a direct descendant of Kaguya Otsutsuki named Toneri Otsutsuki attempts to kidnap Hinata Hyuga but ends up abducting her younger sister Hanabi. Naruto and his allies now mount a rescue mission before finding themselves embroiled in a final battle to decide the fate of everything.', '2014-12-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mksl3tYdyK4', 'Tsuneo Kobayashi', 'Junko Takeuchi, Nana Mizuki, Jun Fukuyama, Chie Nakamura, Showtaro Morikubo'),
(440, 1417, 7.756, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/s8C4whhKtDaJvMDcyiMvx3BIF5F.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/o0IWa75BXyXryNDVqw0xoXZzy1J.jpg', 'es', 'Pan\'s Labyrinth', 'Fantasy', 'Drama', 'War', 'Living with her tyrannical stepfather in a new home with her pregnant mother, 10-year-old Ofelia feels alone until she explores a decaying labyrinth guarded by a mysterious faun who claims to know her destiny. If she wishes to return to her real father, Ofelia must complete three terrifying tasks.', '2006-10-10', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6tYUOAMsydg', 'Guillermo del Toro', 'Ivana Baquero, Sergi López, Maribel Verdú, Ariadna Gil, Doug Jones'),
(441, 396535, 7.754, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vNVFt6dtcqnI7hqa6LFBUibuFiw.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/brnfCYyz8EMbBrHgmh8sCwBi5i1.jpg', 'ko', 'Train to Busan', 'Horror', 'Thriller', 'Action', 'When a zombie virus pushes Korea into a state of emergency, those trapped on an express train to Busan must fight for their own survival.', '2016-07-20', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0_sV9luPnMk', 'Yeon Sang-ho', 'Gong Yoo, Kim Su-an, Jung Yu-mi, Ma Dong-seok, Choi Woo-shik'),
(442, 12444, 7.754, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iGoXIpQb7Pot00EEdwpwPajheZ5.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/AqLcLsGGTzAjm3pCCq0CZCQrp6m.jpg', 'en', 'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', NULL, 'Harry, Ron and Hermione walk away from their last year at Hogwarts to find and destroy the remaining Horcruxes, putting an end to Voldemort\'s bid for immortality. But with Harry\'s beloved Dumbledore dead and Voldemort\'s unscrupulous Death Eaters on the loose, the world is more dangerous than ever.', '2010-11-17', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MxqsmsA8y5k', 'David Yates', 'Daniel Radcliffe, Emma Watson, Rupert Grint, Toby Jones, Helena Bonham Carter'),
(443, 873, 7.753, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ziosRyziefrmEmAMIswpjQzvAur.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rhMpAPvoy1beXd8gA6CvYoCSztj.jpg', 'en', 'The Color Purple', 'Drama', 'History', NULL, 'An epic tale spanning forty years in the life of Celie, an African-American woman living in the South who survives incredible abuse and bigotry. After Celie\'s abusive father marries her off to the equally debasing \'Mister\' Albert Johnson, things go from bad to worse, leaving Celie to find companionship anywhere she can. She perseveres, holding on to her dream of one day being reunited with her sister in Africa.', '1985-12-18', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_h-efLS7VV4', 'Steven Spielberg', 'Danny Glover, Whoopi Goldberg, Margaret Avery, Oprah Winfrey, Willard E. Pugh'),
(444, 273248, 7.752, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jIywvdPjia2t3eKYbjVTcwBQlG8.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7gfDVfaw0VaIkUGiEH13o3TIC7A.jpg', 'en', 'The Hateful Eight', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'Western', 'Bounty hunters seek shelter from a raging blizzard and get caught up in a plot of betrayal and deception.', '2015-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GRG7fAPksbg', 'Quentin Tarantino', 'Samuel L. Jackson, Kurt Russell, Jennifer Jason Leigh, Walton Goggins, Demián Bichir'),
(445, 703, 7.751, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jj46Biz1WYQZoVZfXxeT9u4XRrS.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8n9dYsTbXTykzm2Nuy7R2ftapXQ.jpg', 'en', 'Annie Hall', 'Comedy', 'Drama', 'Romance', 'New York comedian Alvy Singer falls in love with the ditsy Annie Hall.', '1977-04-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H19okah-uCw', 'Woody Allen', 'Diane Keaton, Tony Roberts, Carol Kane, Paul Simon, Shelley Duvall'),
(446, 293310, 7.75, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nOVhX69EAxtSKEEnr5UcSd5UVci.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pttNnC5WsYr3SUpBmJtnN1OkDS9.jpg', 'en', 'Citizenfour', 'Documentary', NULL, NULL, 'In June 2013, Laura Poitras and reporter Glenn Greenwald flew to Hong Kong for the first of many meetings with Edward Snowden. She brought her camera with her.', '2014-10-10', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PX2uyP9QGjs', 'Laura Poitras', 'Edward Snowden, Glenn Greenwald, William Binney, Barack Obama, Jacob Appelbaum'),
(447, 166428, 7.75, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xvx4Yhf0DVH8G4LzNISpMfFBDy2.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/h3KN24PrOheHVYs9ypuOIdFBEpX.jpg', 'en', 'How to Train Your Dragon: The Hidden World', 'Animation', 'Family', 'Adventure', 'As Hiccup fulfills his dream of creating a peaceful dragon utopia, Toothless’ discovery of an untamed, elusive mate draws the Night Fury away. When danger mounts at home and Hiccup’s reign as village chief is tested, both dragon and rider must make impossible decisions to save their kind.', '2019-01-03', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5DEdq57E5ls', 'Dean DeBlois', 'Jay Baruchel, America Ferrera, F. Murray Abraham, Cate Blanchett, Gerard Butler'),
(448, 10229, 7.751, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8lUYMvWdHA0Q0k5F76RQCeCBUkA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uRdJx2p950EobLYuf7Oz39Wk7jd.jpg', 'en', 'A Walk to Remember', 'Drama', 'Romance', NULL, 'When the popular, restless Landon Carter is forced to participate in the school drama production, he falls in love with Jamie Sullivan, the daughter of the town\'s minister. Jamie has a \"to-do\" list for her life, as well as a very big secret she must keep from Landon.', '2002-01-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kq02sBe5xko', 'Adam Shankman', 'Mandy Moore, Shane West, Peter Coyote, Daryl Hannah, Lauren German'),
(449, 374473, 7.749, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nu3WVABXz2W85N6JXTZOT1aWS3b.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2BHjCq5fonp5r16qxGZ9VS3pHtw.jpg', 'en', 'I, Daniel Blake', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'A middle aged carpenter, who requires state welfare after injuring himself, is joined by a single mother in a similar scenario.', '2016-10-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tWaZFvdW7Pc', 'Ken Loach', 'Dave Johns, Hayley Squires, Briana Shann, Dylan McKiernan, Kate Rutter'),
(450, 269149, 7.748, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hlK0e0wAQ3VLuJcsfIYPvb4JVud.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/p2fRZzxla6NoRbIH2KOZq0gHb5S.jpg', 'en', 'Zootopia', 'Animation', 'Adventure', 'Family', 'Determined to prove herself, Officer Judy Hopps, the first bunny on Zootopia\'s police force, jumps at the chance to crack her first case - even if it means partnering with scam-artist fox Nick Wilde to solve the mystery.', '2016-02-11', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jWM0ct-OLsM', 'Byron Howard, Rich Moore', 'Jason Bateman, Ginnifer Goodwin, Idris Elba, Jenny Slate, Nate Torrence'),
(451, 27670, 7.747, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cnhfXiqrJppDvo6nc5QgOAtRp2z.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jBP00fK8DfAhmmc2d6y1nUkhdjY.jpg', 'it', 'Nothing Left to Do But Cry', 'Comedy', NULL, NULL, 'Two 20th-century friends accidentally stumble into the year 1492, where they meet a charming teen and try to alter history.', '1984-12-20', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ezoVaby2rMg', 'Roberto Benigni, Massimo Troisi', 'Massimo Troisi, Roberto Benigni, Amanda Sandrelli, Iris Peynado, Carlo Monni'),
(452, 382591, 7.746, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/aFgtdhuzgI2eqnIVWtRB03x3pnt.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fO0qXJnBJYuWJ5dvWWGXfRF8MXA.jpg', 'fr', 'Two Is a Family', 'Drama', 'Comedy', NULL, 'A man without attachments or responsibilities suddenly finds himself with an abandoned baby and leaves for London to try and find the mother. Eight years later after he and his daughter become inseparable Gloria\'s mother reappears.', '2016-12-07', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QrB7tmqWrAY', 'Hugo Gélin', 'Omar Sy, Gloria Colston, Clémence Poésy, Antoine Bertrand, Ashley Walters'),
(453, 2108, 7.746, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vSqk5BeQ1HvP9wq0rWZyWqiwXeF.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/qpPFF8Sed5lkXngWraJdN8WkwDG.jpg', 'en', 'The Breakfast Club', 'Comedy', 'Drama', NULL, 'Five high school students from different walks of life endure a Saturday detention under a power-hungry principal. The disparate group includes rebel John, princess Claire, outcast Allison, brainy Brian and Andrew, the jock. Each has a chance to tell his or her story, making the others see them a little differently -- and when the day ends, they question whether school will ever be the same.', '1985-02-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OVdr9HiAStI', 'John Hughes', 'Emilio Estevez, Judd Nelson, Molly Ringwald, Anthony Michael Hall, Ally Sheedy'),
