(457, 486589, 7.7, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/MBiKqTsouYqAACLYNDadsjhhC0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nN4Gs3vZAOJ1D6FRtrwbU9VGYwU.jpg', 'ko', 'Red Shoes and the Seven Dwarfs', 'Animation', 'Fantasy', 'Drama', 'Princes who have been turned into Dwarfs seek the red shoes of a lady in order to break the spell, although it will not be easy.', '2019-07-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NB3mZMyxcM0', 'Hong Sung-ho', 'Ahn So-yi, Shin Yong-woo, 권성혁, Yoon Se-woong, 유호한'),
(458, 45269, 7.742, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uQ538BfYLDJh3GXlzRZLo0j7PFj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5eb7l7AE2yU0mvb38fR5qLNhDDH.jpg', 'en', 'The King\'s Speech', 'Drama', 'History', NULL, 'The King\'s Speech tells the story of the man who became King George VI, the father of Queen Elizabeth II. After his brother abdicates, George (\'Bertie\') reluctantly assumes the throne. Plagued by a dreaded stutter and considered unfit to be king, Bertie engages the help of an unorthodox speech therapist named Lionel Logue. Through a set of unexpected techniques, and as a result of an unlikely friendship, Bertie is able to find his voice and boldly lead the country into war.', '2010-11-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OpH8kO1AyVA', 'Tom Hooper', 'Colin Firth, Geoffrey Rush, Helena Bonham Carter, Guy Pearce, Timothy Spall'),
(459, 525, 7.7, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rhYJKOt6UrQq7JQgLyQcSWW5R86.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/bk2fTuIhQIvdAA3RbnrnvLvuaTc.jpg', 'en', 'The Blues Brothers', 'Music', 'Comedy', 'Action', 'Jake Blues, just released from prison, puts his old band back together to save the Catholic home where he and his brother Elwood were raised.', '1980-06-16', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zaCGMiFRJEA', 'John Landis', 'Dan Aykroyd, John Belushi, James Brown, Cab Calloway, Ray Charles'),
(460, 603692, 7.742, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vZloFAK7NmvMGKE7VkF5UHaz0I.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7I6VUdPj6tQECNHdviJkUHD2u89.jpg', 'en', 'John Wick: Chapter 4', 'Action', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'With the price on his head ever increasing, John Wick uncovers a path to defeating The High Table. But before he can earn his freedom, Wick must face off against a new enemy with powerful alliances across the globe and forces that turn old friends into foes.', '2023-03-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yjRHZEUamCc', 'Chad Stahelski', 'Keanu Reeves, Donnie Yen, Bill Skarsgård, Ian McShane, Laurence Fishburne'),
(461, 12429, 7.74, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yp8vEZflGynlEylxEesbYasc06i.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/shqLeIkqPAAXM8iT6wVDiXUYz1p.jpg', 'ja', 'Ponyo', 'Animation', 'Fantasy', 'Family', 'When Sosuke, a young boy who lives on a clifftop overlooking the sea, rescues a stranded goldfish named Ponyo, he discovers more than he bargained for. Ponyo is a curious, energetic young creature who yearns to be human, but even as she causes chaos around the house, her father, a powerful sorcerer, schemes to return Ponyo to the sea.', '2008-07-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HvddJqBYrc8', 'Hayao Miyazaki', 'Yuria Kozuki, Hiroki Doi, George Tokoro, Tomoko Yamaguchi, Yûki Amami'),
(462, 322, 7.739, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hCHVDbo6XJGj3r2i4hVjKhE0GKF.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4ycpMe25LYpzGW42U9amyW9gM53.jpg', 'en', 'Mystic River', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'Drama', 'The lives of three men who were childhood friends are shattered when one of them suffers a family tragedy.', '2003-10-07', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W7NktJhrRYQ', 'Clint Eastwood', 'Sean Penn, Tim Robbins, Kevin Bacon, Laurence Fishburne, Marcia Gay Harden'),
(463, 49046, 7.738, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2IRjbi9cADuDMKmHdLK7LaqQDKA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xBwtP27cx8WfjHJVFkpuV6F1RES.jpg', 'de', 'All Quiet on the Western Front', 'Drama', 'War', 'Action', 'Paul Baumer and his friends Albert and Muller, egged on by romantic dreams of heroism, voluntarily enlist in the German army. Full of excitement and patriotic fervour, the boys enthusiastically march into a war they believe in. But once on the Western Front, they discover the soul-destroying horror of World War I.', '2022-10-07', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hf8EYbVxtCY', 'Edward Berger', 'Felix Kammerer, Albrecht Schuch, Aaron Hilmer, Moritz Klaus, Adrian Grünewald'),
(464, 40662, 7.7, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7lmHqHg1rG9b4U8MjuyQjmJ7Qm0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jGb3kBZlknSGTTNlk6cdZldnh2m.jpg', 'en', 'Batman: Under the Red Hood', 'Science Fiction', 'Crime', 'Action', 'One part vigilante, one part criminal kingpin, Red Hood begins cleaning up Gotham with the efficiency of Batman, but without following the same ethical code.', '2010-07-27', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EcFghlzjEak', 'Brandon Vietti', 'Bruce Greenwood, Jensen Ackles, Neil Patrick Harris, Jason Isaacs, John DiMaggio'),
