(479, 506574, 7.722, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7IRy0iHdaS0JI3ng4ZYlk5gLSFn.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/p0boFm5Z1HzO6LHMBuLYUM48iVV.jpg', 'en', 'Descendants 3', 'Family', 'TV Movie', 'Adventure', 'The teenagers of Disney\'s most infamous villains return to the Isle of the Lost to recruit a new batch of villainous offspring to join them at Auradon Prep.', '2019-08-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8jpvcD_LkK4', 'Kenny Ortega', 'Dove Cameron, Cameron Boyce, Sofia Carson, Booboo Stewart, Mitchell Hope'),
(480, 451945, 7.721, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/azLtGx5ZhdTSP2b4oNLWtiE51OW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1pyUrlbTVCkGkcu7LsGMqxuCtkP.jpg', 'fr', 'BPM (Beats per Minute)', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Paris, in the early 1990s: a group of young activists is desperately tied to finding the cure against an unknown lethal disease. They target the pharmaceutical labs that are retaining potential cures, and multiply direct actions, with the hope of saving their lives as well as the ones of future generations.', '2017-08-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4GzCfjF0vDU', 'Robin Campillo', 'Nahuel Pérez Biscayart, Arnaud Valois, Adèle Haenel, Antoine Reinartz, Félix Maritaud'),
