(482, 672, 7.721, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sdEOH0992YZ0QSxgXNIGLq1ToUi.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yHzyPJrVqlTySQ9mc379yxrLBYQ.jpg', 'en', 'Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', NULL, 'Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on a wall announces: The Chamber Of Secrets Has Been Opened. To save Hogwarts will require all of Harry, Ron and Hermione’s magical abilities and courage.', '2002-11-13', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nE11U5iBnH0', 'Chris Columbus', 'Daniel Radcliffe, Rupert Grint, Emma Watson, Kenneth Branagh, Toby Jones'),
(483, 16052, 7.72, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/j8xX3yBAFOayfSaImgLZPnAcdWz.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kcBlY5FasH8ti150aYExULw53ui.jpg', 'en', 'Selena', 'Drama', 'Music', 'History', 'In this biographical drama, Selena Quintanilla is born into a musical Mexican-American family in Texas. Her father, Abraham, realizes that his young daughter is talented and begins performing with her at small venues. She finds success and falls for her guitarist, Chris Perez, who draws the ire of her father. Seeking mainstream stardom, Selena begins recording an English-language album which, tragically, she would never complete.', '1997-03-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RzePZay7fbQ', 'Gregory Nava', 'Jennifer Lopez, Jackie Guerra, Constance Marie, Alex Meneses, Jon Seda'),
(484, 205, 7.7, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/p3pHw85UMZPegfMZBA6dZ06yarm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ljEdpkceJ9b3TEcTVQISS0Goft0.jpg', 'en', 'Hotel Rwanda', 'Drama', 'History', 'War', 'Inspired by true events, this film takes place in Rwanda in the 1990s when more than a million Tutsis were killed in a genocide that went mostly unnoticed by the rest of the world. Hotel owner Paul Rusesabagina houses over a thousand refuges in his hotel in attempt to save their lives.', '2004-12-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2x8UzELvKlY', 'Terry George', 'Don Cheadle, Sophie Okonedo, Nick Nolte, Fana Mokoena, Joaquin Phoenix'),
(485, 766507, 7.717, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ujr5pztc1oitbe7ViMUOilFaJ7s.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vgatT6hiEf4EquZ1k0uU1Ft5XdI.jpg', 'en', 'Prey', 'Thriller', 'Action', 'Science Fiction', 'When danger threatens her camp, the fierce and highly skilled Comanche warrior Naru sets out to protect her people. But the prey she stalks turns out to be a highly evolved alien predator with a technically advanced arsenal.', '2022-08-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wZ7LytagKlc', 'Dan Trachtenberg', 'Amber Midthunder, Dakota Beavers, Michelle Thrush, Stormee Kipp, Julian Black Antelope'),
