(533, 333339, 7.6, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pU1ULUq8D3iRxl1fdX2lZIzdHuI.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5a7lMDn3nAj2ByO0X1fg6BhUphR.jpg', 'en', 'Ready Player One', 'Adventure', 'Action', 'Science Fiction', 'When the creator of a popular video game system dies, a virtual contest is created to compete for his fortune.', '2018-03-28', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1hrwbc5qCZ4', 'Steven Spielberg', 'Tye Sheridan, Olivia Cooke, Ben Mendelsohn, Lena Waithe, T.J. Miller'),
(534, 244267, 7.599, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2P31jhd1dWUAPD8dmnSrwkQ8CNN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/x8qNQSvvqd2PE15Pm6tmnXH0584.jpg', 'en', 'I Origins', 'Science Fiction', 'Drama', NULL, 'A molecular biologist\'s study of the human eye has far-reaching implications about humanity\'s scientific and spiritual beliefs.', '2014-07-18', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sEGppIgwKf0', 'Mike Cahill', 'Michael Pitt, Brit Marling, Astrid Bergès-Frisbey, Steven Yeun, Archie Panjabi'),
(536, 3580, 7.597, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iECXjFF8JkTnNJvik14WbPpc9s9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yWs9QUP2kamsnfdV4cloxLM5RUw.jpg', 'en', 'Changeling', 'Crime', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'Christine Collins is overjoyed when her kidnapped son is brought back home. But when Christine suspects that the boy returned to her isn\'t her child, the police captain has her committed to an asylum.', '2008-10-24', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IF5hwg4FNEU', 'Clint Eastwood', 'Angelina Jolie, John Malkovich, Jeffrey Donovan, Michael Kelly, Colm Feore'),
(537, 910, 7.597, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/lraHo9D8c0YWfxsKqT5P5sVqMKN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1fMD4KvZ4cR04aQo6hH6R5NdIH8.jpg', 'en', 'The Big Sleep', 'Mystery', 'Crime', 'Thriller', 'Private Investigator Philip Marlowe is hired by wealthy General Sternwood regarding a matter involving his youngest daughter Carmen. Before the complex case is over, Marlowe sees murder, blackmail, deception, and what might be love.', '1946-08-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HiAEX4Y6jEs', 'Howard Hawks', 'Humphrey Bogart, Lauren Bacall, John Ridgely, Martha Vickers, Elisha Cook Jr.'),
(538, 863, 7.597, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/2MFIhZAW0CVlEQrFyqwa4U6zqJP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/91qfG6VaxRsCh1SbIi1w2vxknsL.jpg', 'en', 'Toy Story 2', 'Animation', 'Comedy', 'Family', 'Andy heads off to Cowboy Camp, leaving his toys to their own devices. Things shift into high gear when an obsessive toy collector named Al McWhiggen, owner of Al\'s Toy Barn kidnaps Woody. Andy\'s toys mount a daring rescue mission, Buzz Lightyear meets his match and Woody has to decide where he and his heart truly belong.', '1999-10-30', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xNWSGRD5CzU', 'John Lasseter', 'Tom Hanks, Tim Allen, Joan Cusack, Kelsey Grammer, Don Rickles'),
(539, 283587, 7.596, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1D4vcJmJc58WXarpRtwgd2do9Rg.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vDfbeUK3OhoeyQRlUODwfSy6tyE.jpg', 'en', 'Beasts of No Nation', 'Drama', 'War', NULL, 'Based on the experiences of Agu, a child fighting in the civil war of an unnamed, fictional West African country. Follows Agu\'s journey as he\'s forced to join a group of soldiers. While he fears his commander and many of the men around him, his fledgling childhood has been brutally shattered by the war raging through his country, and he is at first torn between conflicting revulsion and fascination.', '2015-09-11', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2xb9Ty-1frw', 'Cary Joji Fukunaga', 'Abraham Attah, Idris Elba, Emmanuel Nii Adom Quaye, Opeyemi Fagbohungbe, Emmanuel Affadzi'),
(540, 222935, 7.596, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ep7dF4QR4Mm39LI958V0XbwE0hK.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/oQaVV7p916HO5MDI820zzs1pin9.jpg', 'en', 'The Fault in Our Stars', 'Romance', 'Drama', NULL, 'Despite the tumor-shrinking medical miracle that has bought her a few years, Hazel has never been anything but terminal, her final chapter inscribed upon diagnosis. But when a patient named Augustus Waters suddenly appears at Cancer Kid Support Group, Hazel\'s story is about to be completely rewritten.', '2014-05-16', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Ixw15DE-xY', 'Josh Boone', 'Shailene Woodley, Ansel Elgort, Nat Wolff, Laura Dern, Sam Trammell'),
(541, 14784, 7.595, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jUx4P4Q1VsQ07rLz7sOlSyNm4F3.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8yZyGXteuM1kHUnrDPfG7QqMgUS.jpg', 'en', 'The Fall', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', 'Drama', 'In a hospital on the outskirts of 1920s Los Angeles, an injured stuntman begins to tell a fellow patient, a little girl with a broken arm, a fantastic story about 5 mythical heroes. Thanks to his fractured state of mind and her vivid imagination, the line between fiction and reality starts to blur as the tale advances.', '2006-09-09', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OTn5XUFP_iA', 'Tarsem Singh', 'Lee Pace, Catinca Untaru, Jeetu Verma, Marcus Wesley, Leo Bill'),
(542, 71, 7.6, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nOr5diUZxphmAD3li9aiILyI28F.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/urzflyf41uySpgciGHdQzpcaMOY.jpg', 'en', 'Billy Elliot', 'Drama', 'Comedy', 'Music', 'County Durham, England, 1984. The miners\' strike has started and the police have started coming up from Bethnal Green, starting a class war with the lower classes suffering. Caught in the middle of the conflict is 11-year old Billy Elliot, who, after leaving his boxing club for the day, stumbles upon a ballet class and finds out that he\'s naturally talented. He practices with his teacher Mrs. Wilkinson for an upcoming audition in Newcastle-upon Tyne for the royal Ballet school in London.', '2000-09-28', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qMZkyG4skCU', 'Stephen Daldry', 'Jamie Bell, Gary Lewis, Julie Walters, Jean Heywood, Jamie Draven'),
(543, 284053, 7.593, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rzRwTcFvttcN1ZpX2xv4j3tSdJu.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kaIfm5ryEOwYg8mLbq8HkPuM1Fo.jpg', 'en', 'Thor: Ragnarok', 'Action', 'Adventure', 'Science Fiction', 'Thor is imprisoned on the other side of the universe and finds himself in a race against time to get back to Asgard to stop Ragnarok, the destruction of his home-world and the end of Asgardian civilization, at the hands of a powerful new threat, the ruthless Hela.', '2017-10-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ue80QwXMRHg', 'Taika Waititi', 'Chris Hemsworth, Mark Ruffalo, Tom Hiddleston, Cate Blanchett, Idris Elba'),
(544, 244, 7.593, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/lHlnxKL5GbgRibyRFI7n1Ey850i.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7hDdW3C17pi4MdSeYXs8bwIVA78.jpg', 'en', 'King Kong', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', 'Horror', 'Adventurous filmmaker Carl Denham sets out to produce a motion picture unlike anything the world has seen before. Alongside his leading lady Ann Darrow and his first mate Jack Driscoll, they arrive on an island and discover a legendary creature said to be neither beast nor man. Denham captures the monster to be displayed on Broadway as King Kong, the eighth wonder of the world.', '1933-03-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vWUL5m6c0YM', 'Ernest B. Schoedsack, Merian C. Cooper', 'Robert Armstrong, Fay Wray, Bruce Cabot, Frank Reicher, Victor Wong'),
(545, 915935, 7.592, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kQs6keheMwCxJxrzV83VUwFtHkB.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kszooR7v1TLFM4pzx6IkKq2jDAN.jpg', 'fr', 'Anatomy of a Fall', 'Thriller', 'Mystery', 'Crime', 'A woman is suspected of her husband\'s murder, and their blind son faces a moral dilemma as the sole witness.', '2023-08-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_MdTMA0PetA', 'Justine Triet', 'Sandra Hüller, Swann Arlaud, Milo Machado-Graner, Antoine Reinartz, Samuel Theis'),
(546, 431693, 7.591, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/30YacPAcxpNemhhwX0PVUl9pVA3.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uG1v9Hk1XKICd6IJChRR20mBh8i.jpg', 'en', 'Spies in Disguise', 'Animation', 'Action', 'Adventure', 'Super spy Lance Sterling and scientist Walter Beckett are almost exact opposites. Lance is smooth, suave and debonair. Walter is… not. But what Walter lacks in social skills he makes up for in smarts and invention, creating the awesome gadgets Lance uses on his epic missions. But when events take an unexpected turn, Walter and Lance suddenly have to rely on each other in a whole new way.', '2019-12-04', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9eY2W7uUkDE', 'Troy Quane, Nick Bruno', 'Will Smith, Tom Holland, Ben Mendelsohn, Rashida Jones, Karen Gillan'),
(547, 284427, 7.59, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/oR3tbNzJMJmCKS5O5fanU9yxIOk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1g6Y3Np97aYuozVaKUoKR6mMCtb.jpg', 'de', 'Who Am I', 'Thriller', NULL, NULL, 'Benjamin, a young German computer whiz, is invited to join a subversive hacker group that wants to be noticed on the world\'s stage.', '2014-09-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5vnjheCqRIs', 'Baran bo Odar', 'Tom Schilling, Elyas M\'Barek, Wotan Wilke Möhring, Antoine Monot Jr., Hannah Herzsprung'),
(548, 4951, 7.59, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ujERk3aKABXU3NDXOAxEQYTHe9A.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yvPbncYhMu9FfTjDhq0N5lgnVkO.jpg', 'en', '10 Things I Hate About You', 'Comedy', 'Romance', 'Drama', 'On the first day at his new school, Cameron instantly falls for Bianca, the gorgeous girl of his dreams. The only problem is that Bianca is forbidden to date until her ill-tempered, completely un-dateable older sister Kat goes out, too. In an attempt to solve his problem, Cameron singles out the only guy who could possibly be a match for Kat: a mysterious bad boy with a nasty reputation of his own.', '1999-03-30', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GbWQ_VXek6A', 'Gil Junger', 'Heath Ledger, Julia Stiles, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Larisa Oleynik, David Krumholtz'),
(549, 306819, 7.588, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mXZZIacI5FC8thzSC0lgQBQ2uAX.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/reOdKBPXT9TpwyYnGGyKxG3jXe6.jpg', 'en', 'The Danish Girl', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'When Gerda Wegener asks her husband Einar to fill in as a portrait model, Einar discovers the person she\'s meant to be and begins living her life as Lili Elbe. Having realized her true self and with Gerda\'s love and support, Lili embarks on a groundbreaking journey as a transgender pioneer.', '2015-11-27', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3qEphMRGIc', 'Tom Hooper', 'Eddie Redmayne, Alicia Vikander, Matthias Schoenaerts, Ben Whishaw, Sebastian Koch'),
(550, 21575, 7.589, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/x9Jb8kewBHPzjTtgCQvoQoDsy4d.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7en9qwF88VfxPXsN6azHmUxRBNy.jpg', 'fr', 'A Prophet', 'Crime', 'Drama', NULL, 'Sentenced to six years in prison, Malik El Djebena is alone in the world and can neither read nor write. On his arrival at the prison, he seems younger and more brittle than the others detained there. At once he falls under the sway of a group of Corsicans who enforce their rule in the prison. As the \'missions\' go by, he toughens himself and wins the confidence of the Corsican group.', '2009-08-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J_16ZOjGkhE', 'Jacques Audiard', 'Tahar Rahim, Niels Arestrup, Adel Bencherif, Hichem Yacoubi, Reda Kateb'),
(551, 9377, 7.589, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9LTQNCvoLsKXP0LtaKAaYVtRaQL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jehzP4JKiFzgTWIaASLFOJocJke.jpg', 'en', 'Ferris Bueller\'s Day Off', 'Comedy', NULL, NULL, 'After high school slacker Ferris Bueller successfully fakes an illness in order to skip school for the day, he goes on a series of adventures throughout Chicago with his girlfriend Sloane and best friend Cameron, all the while trying to outwit his wily school principal and fed-up sister.', '1986-06-11', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GDttaV80_BM', 'John Hughes', 'Matthew Broderick, Alan Ruck, Mia Sara, Jeffrey Jones, Jennifer Grey'),
(552, 630, 7.6, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pfAZFD7I2hxW9HCChTuAzsdE6UX.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nRsr98MFztBGm532hCVMGXV6qOp.jpg', 'en', 'The Wizard of Oz', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', 'Family', 'Young Dorothy finds herself in a magical world where she makes friends with a lion, a scarecrow and a tin man as they make their way along the yellow brick road to talk with the Wizard and ask for the things they miss most in their lives. The Wicked Witch of the West is the only thing that could stop them.', '1939-08-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b_A2twyZevo', 'Victor Fleming', 'Judy Garland, Ray Bolger, Jack Haley, Bert Lahr, Frank Morgan'),
(553, 616, 7.6, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/lsasOSgYI85EHygtT5SvcxtZVYT.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/z354BaTVzKj7E60WLzDoSmUuO4u.jpg', 'en', 'The Last Samurai', 'Drama', 'Action', 'War', 'Nathan Algren is an American hired to instruct the Japanese army in the ways of modern warfare, which finds him learning to respect the samurai and the honorable principles that rule them. Pressed to destroy the samurai\'s way of life in the name of modernization and open trade, Algren decides to become an ultimate warrior himself and to fight for their right to exist.', '2003-12-05', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QZpQrc0R6J0', 'Edward Zwick', 'Tom Cruise, Ken Watanabe, Timothy Spall, Tony Goldwyn, Hiroyuki Sanada'),
(554, 707886, 7.587, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/Af2jt7m9GLFpR4V11xOsFmT8OKD.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fZBQOScjDT8TAipEyCkLVeDTu5c.jpg', 'en', 'Feel the Beat', 'Comedy', 'Music', 'Drama', 'After failing to make it on Broadway, April returns to her hometown and reluctantly begins training a misfit group of young dancers for a competition.', '2020-06-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PhLSDnxLp-M', 'Elissa Down', 'Sofia Carson, Wolfgang Novogratz, Donna Lynne Champlin, Enrico Colantoni, Dennis Andres'),
