(590, 1372, 7.546, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tnLxPpajkbVdbQl5B9CuD7sSpz9.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/466zklOlxKDXID4ejaIXu3PN5nV.jpg', 'en', 'Blood Diamond', 'Drama', 'Thriller', 'Action', 'An ex-mercenary turned smuggler. A Mende fisherman. Amid the explosive civil war overtaking 1999 Sierra Leone, these men join for two desperate missions: recovering a rare pink diamond of immense value and rescuing the fisherman\'s son, conscripted as a child soldier into the brutal rebel forces ripping a swath of torture and bloodshed countrywide.', '2006-12-08', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YG_a8lw512A', 'Edward Zwick', 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Djimon Hounsou, Jennifer Connelly, Kagiso Kuypers, Arnold Vosloo'),
