(612, 228150, 7.532, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pfte7wdMobMF4CVHuOxyu6oqeeA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kdbLf3aTQsEXqYlH9vA4fzmnSFz.jpg', 'en', 'Fury', 'War', 'Drama', 'Action', 'In the last months of World War II, as the Allies make their final push in the European theatre, a battle-hardened U.S. Army sergeant named \'Wardaddy\' commands a Sherman tank called \'Fury\' and its five-man crew on a deadly mission behind enemy lines. Outnumbered and outgunned, Wardaddy and his men face overwhelming odds in their heroic attempts to strike at the heart of Nazi Germany.', '2014-10-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=09w9MTtZDEM', 'David Ayer', 'Brad Pitt, Shia LaBeouf, Logan Lerman, Michael Peña, Jon Bernthal'),
(613, 59436, 7.532, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4wBG5kbfagTQclETblPRRGihk0I.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/b5bcKhvN6VP82U5ztNdPfOLiolD.jpg', 'en', 'Midnight in Paris', 'Fantasy', 'Comedy', 'Romance', 'While on a trip to Paris with his fiancée\'s family, a nostalgic screenwriter finds himself mysteriously going back to the 1920s every day at midnight.', '2011-05-11', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FAfR8omt-CY', 'Woody Allen', 'Owen Wilson, Rachel McAdams, Kathy Bates, Kurt Fuller, Adrien Brody'),
(614, 12163, 7.532, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/6OTR8dSoNGjWohJNo3UhIGd3Tj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wcJmFsz8RqIhozMwvU81hreTX4i.jpg', 'en', 'The Wrestler', 'Drama', 'Romance', NULL, 'Aging wrestler Randy \"The Ram\" Robinson is long past his prime but still ready and rarin\' to go on the pro-wrestling circuit. After a particularly brutal beating, however, Randy hangs up his tights, pursues a serious relationship with a long-in-the-tooth stripper, and tries to reconnect with his estranged daughter. But he can\'t resist the lure of the ring and readies himself for a comeback.', '2008-09-07', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qjhGZhRJ3j0', 'Darren Aronofsky', 'Mickey Rourke, Marisa Tomei, Evan Rachel Wood, Mark Margolis, Todd Barry'),
(615, 281957, 7.531, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tSaBkriE7TpbjFoQUFXuikoz0dF.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mNQtUJv1F3u0uSKILFrGjIHqkxx.jpg', 'en', 'The Revenant', 'Western', 'Drama', 'Adventure', 'In the 1820s, a frontiersman, Hugh Glass, sets out on a path of vengeance against those who left him for dead after a bear mauling.', '2015-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LoebZZ8K5N0', 'Alejandro González Iñárritu', 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Tom Hardy, Domhnall Gleeson, Will Poulter, Forrest Goodluck'),
(616, 1430, 7.531, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5AlgeysilsfLdEwlTlYO7fqgsLn.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yhgxyvKQrKdkxRz1ljGBMOxYHB7.jpg', 'en', 'Bowling for Columbine', 'Documentary', 'Drama', NULL, 'This is not a film about gun control. It is a film about the fearful heart and soul of the United States, and the 280 million Americans lucky enough to have the right to a constitutionally protected Uzi. From a look at the Columbine High School security camera tapes to the home of Oscar-winning NRA President Charlton Heston, from a young man who makes homemade napalm with The Anarchist\'s Cookbook to the murder of a six-year-old girl by another six-year-old. Bowling for Columbine is a journey through the US, through our past, hoping to discover why our pursuit of happiness is so riddled with violence.', '2002-10-09', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AElSP38H8OE', 'Michael Moore', 'George H. W. Bush, George W. Bush, Charlton Heston, Jacobo Árbenz, Mike Bradley'),
(617, 127585, 7.5, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tYfijzolzgoMOtegh1Y7j2Enorg.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fctQU5MoXgJ5pNMljFzlEFXwfSu.jpg', 'en', 'X-Men: Days of Future Past', 'Action', 'Adventure', 'Science Fiction', 'The ultimate X-Men ensemble fights a war for the survival of the species across two time periods as they join forces with their younger selves in an epic battle that must change the past – to save our future.', '2014-05-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gsjtg7m1MMM', 'Bryan Singer', 'Hugh Jackman, James McAvoy, Michael Fassbender, Patrick Stewart, Ian McKellen'),
(618, 10778, 7.53, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gQHBLxJmakVO1h7VnTHwnVplXZs.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zHKEgUrLn8wRrBmKRPIq5sFPrvV.jpg', 'en', 'The Man Who Wasn\'t There', 'Crime', 'Drama', NULL, 'A tale of murder, crime and punishment set in the summer of 1949. Ed Crane, a barber in a small California town, is dissatisfied with his life, but his wife Doris\' infidelity and a mysterious opportunity presents him with a chance to change it.', '2001-10-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vjO8u_9CqXI', 'Joel Coen', 'Billy Bob Thornton, Frances McDormand, Michael Badalucco, James Gandolfini, Katherine Borowitz'),
(619, 11544, 7.528, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/m13Vbzv7R2GMAl3GXFrkmMEgCFQ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cxDFAic9FXPPJt2MdfX4ijVh3eC.jpg', 'en', 'Lilo & Stitch', 'Animation', 'Family', NULL, 'As Stitch, a runaway genetic experiment from a faraway planet, wreaks havoc on the Hawaiian Islands, he becomes the mischievous adopted alien \"puppy\" of an independent little girl named Lilo and learns about loyalty, friendship, and ʻohana, the Hawaiian tradition of family.', '2002-06-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wAtaSKQ4-T0', 'Dean DeBlois, Chris Sanders', 'Daveigh Chase, Tia Carrere, David Ogden Stiers, Kevin McDonald, Ving Rhames'),
(620, 592, 7.5, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pOCzGvGQkwW8wdLC7v4OE7ivIV7.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fVJZYpzVTKo0vXmar9NnRMV0Qcn.jpg', 'en', 'The Conversation', 'Crime', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'Surveillance expert Harry Caul is hired by a mysterious client\'s brusque aide to tail a young couple. Tracking the pair through San Francisco\'s Union Square, Caul and his associate Stan manage to record a cryptic conversation between them. Tormented by memories of a previous case that ended badly, Caul becomes obsessed with the resulting tape, trying to determine if the couple is in danger.', '1974-04-07', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mDgKPQWyjRk', 'Francis Ford Coppola', 'Gene Hackman, John Cazale, Allen Garfield, Frederic Forrest, Cindy Williams'),
