(672, 370172, 7.4, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iUgygt3fscRoKWCV1d0C7FbM9TP.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/18Eca3pEMrdk6GkmKWdf02jWpmo.jpg', 'en', 'No Time to Die', 'Action', 'Adventure', 'Thriller', 'Bond has left active service and is enjoying a tranquil life in Jamaica. His peace is short-lived when his old friend Felix Leiter from the CIA turns up asking for help. The mission to rescue a kidnapped scientist turns out to be far more treacherous than expected, leading Bond onto the trail of a mysterious villain armed with dangerous new technology.', '2021-09-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_gD9-Oa0fg', 'Cary Joji Fukunaga', 'Daniel Craig, Léa Seydoux, Rami Malek, Lashana Lynch, Ralph Fiennes'),
