(676, 9462, 7.377, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/m7AIITQ624sfldI4SsX4htXPH1f.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/et9G1ftzPo3KDolLEnOEbxA44oP.jpg', 'cn', 'The Way of the Dragon', 'Action', 'Crime', NULL, 'Tang Lung arrives in Rome to help his cousins in the restaurant business. They are being pressured to sell their property to the syndicate, who will stop at nothing to get what they want. When Tang arrives he poses a new threat to the syndicate, and they are unable to defeat him. The syndicate boss hires the best Japanese and European martial artists to fight Tang, but he easily finishes them off.', '1972-12-30', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=72giNDkKhSE', 'Bruce Lee', 'Bruce Lee, Nora Miao, Chuck Norris, Wei Ping-ao, Huang Tsung-Hsun'),
(677, 866398, 7.374, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/A7EByudX0eOzlkQ2FIbogzyazm2.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4MCKNAc6AbWjEsM2h9Xc29owo4z.jpg', 'en', 'The Beekeeper', 'Action', NULL, NULL, 'One man\'s campaign for vengeance takes on national stakes after he is revealed to be a former operative of a powerful and clandestine organization known as Beekeepers.', '2024-01-08', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CHKn-yDCE2w', 'David Ayer', 'Jason Statham, Emmy Raver-Lampman, Bobby Naderi, Josh Hutcherson, Jeremy Irons'),
(678, 16320, 7.376, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/4sqUOaPFoP2W81mq1UYqZqf5WzA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/csGprKcRxt7SDpsrKiwxpgLdEsx.jpg', 'en', 'Serenity', 'Science Fiction', 'Action', 'Adventure', 'When the renegade crew of Serenity agrees to hide a fugitive on their ship, they find themselves in an action-packed battle between the relentless military might of a totalitarian regime who will destroy anything – or anyone – to get the girl back and the bloodthirsty creatures who roam the uncharted areas of space. But... the greatest danger of all may be on their ship.', '2005-09-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zybHB2V27G8', 'Joss Whedon', 'Nathan Fillion, Summer Glau, Gina Torres, Alan Tudyk, Morena Baccarin'),
(679, 476299, 7.375, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rEU5U8ztBQnOS2BMD8ohdGtqKgo.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gl3RKxaM65gyrvRoG3MffTYBoo5.jpg', 'en', 'Ghostland', 'Horror', 'Mystery', 'Thriller', 'A mother of two inherits a home from her aunt. On the first night in the new home she is confronted with murderous intruders and fights for her daughters’ lives. Sixteen years later the daughters reunite at the house, and that is when things get strange...', '2018-03-14', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q8KqeolPt2w', 'Pascal Laugier', 'Crystal Reed, Mylène Farmer, Anastasia Phillips, Emilia Jones, Taylor Hickson'),
(680, 1245, 7.375, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uDGDtqSvuch324WnM7Ukdp1bCAQ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/vFhxd3Z1zaV3Yu5XLpvWzSxJCe8.jpg', 'en', 'The Remains of the Day', 'Drama', 'Romance', NULL, 'A rule bound head butler\'s world of manners and decorum in the household he maintains is tested by the arrival of a housekeeper who falls in love with him in post-WWI Britain. The possibility of romance and his master\'s cultivation of ties with the Nazi cause challenge his carefully maintained veneer of servitude.', '1993-11-05', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jALmEb72beg', 'James Ivory', 'Anthony Hopkins, Emma Thompson, James Fox, Christopher Reeve, Hugh Grant'),
(681, 985, 7.373, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mxveW3mGVc0DzLdOmtkZsgd7c3B.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ApB0mF2d5Oqioi3yxjuogiotSLI.jpg', 'en', 'Eraserhead', 'Horror', NULL, NULL, 'First-time father Henry Spencer tries to survive his industrial environment, his angry girlfriend, and the unbearable screams of his newly born mutant child.', '1978-02-03', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J0Eq5GtCYdA', 'David Lynch', 'Jack Nance, Charlotte Stewart, Allen Joseph, Jeanne Bates, Judith Roberts'),
(682, 249164, 7.373, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7Twh8h3Wh7GC9npTAEUThgkxkWL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xxmf2JWcBt7E8nBrIu0JXK3CX4.jpg', 'en', 'If I Stay', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Mia Hall, a talented young cellist, thought the most difficult decision she would ever have to make would be whether to pursue her musical dreams at prestigious Juilliard or follow her heart to be with the love of her life, Adam, a rock singer/guitarist. However, a car wreck changes everything in an instant, and now Mia\'s life hangs in the balance. Suspended between life and death, Mia faces a choice that will decide her future.', '2014-08-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wH6PNeTy6Nc', 'R.J. Cutler', 'Chloë Grace Moretz, Jamie Blackley, Liana Liberato, Mireille Enos, Joshua Leonard'),
(683, 157354, 7.373, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/oXSy3nEKFtfw5iRxdG8ouEFAnxs.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/u0nAnvRdzAGgDYLyfIbAUBDOcpb.jpg', 'en', 'Fruitvale Station', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Oakland, California. Young Afro-American Oscar Grant crosses paths with family members, friends, enemies and strangers before facing his fate on the platform at Fruitvale Station, in the early morning hours of New Year\'s Day 2009.', '2013-07-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vHkKUPHn8TE', 'Ryan Coogler', 'Michael B. Jordan, Melonie Diaz, Octavia Spencer, Kevin Durand, Chad Michael Murray'),
(684, 493529, 7.373, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/v7UF7ypAqjsFZFdjksjQ7IUpXdn.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/oblUNeHlwV3VsjB5ITMlco5ZSOF.jpg', 'en', 'Dungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves', 'Adventure', 'Fantasy', 'Comedy', 'A charming thief and a band of unlikely adventurers undertake an epic heist to retrieve a lost relic, but things go dangerously awry when they run afoul of the wrong people.', '2023-03-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LLOLEBlVIA', 'John Francis Daley, Jonathan Goldstein', 'Chris Pine, Michelle Rodriguez, Justice Smith, Sophia Lillis, Hugh Grant'),
(685, 15080, 7.373, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tOSnFE9e82iH3ZAzSTtuOkBsabJ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jsIxoKIuH6lLt4Y3NW7Tf1BwcIO.jpg', 'ja', 'Only Yesterday', 'Animation', 'Drama', 'Romance', 'In lyrical switches between the present and the past, Taeko contemplates the arc of her life, and wonders if she has been true to the dreams of her childhood self.', '1991-07-20', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OfkQlZArxw0', 'Isao Takahata', 'Miki Imai, Toshiro Yanagiba, Yoko Honna, Mayumi Izuka, Chie Kitagawa'),
(686, 1052, 7.372, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iVtUdWsT6Ed2DK762zZxjaQAdHy.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1TOB9YhatqxIj5IMIZmnrwdL7AL.jpg', 'en', 'Blow-Up', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'Thriller', 'A successful mod photographer in London whose world is bounded by fashion, pop music, marijuana, and easy sex, feels his life is boring and despairing. But in the course of a single day he unknowingly captures a death on film.', '1966-12-18', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PRENEOHlcbw', 'Michelangelo Antonioni', 'David Hemmings, Vanessa Redgrave, Sarah Miles, John Castle, Veruschka von Lehndorff'),
(687, 65754, 7.37, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8bokS83zGdhaXgN9tjidUKmAftW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dNFbrnF0mIBm0rClbfEFWTtsgMP.jpg', 'en', 'The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'Mystery', 'Disgraced journalist Mikael Blomkvist investigates the disappearance of a weary patriarch\'s niece from 40 years ago. He is aided by the pierced, tattooed, punk computer hacker named Lisbeth Salander. As they work together in the investigation, Blomkvist and Salander uncover immense corruption beyond anything they have ever imagined.', '2011-12-14', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=svucpVzRBD4', 'David Fincher', 'Daniel Craig, Rooney Mara, Christopher Plummer, Stellan Skarsgård, Robin Wright'),
(688, 9504, 7.37, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nGZCeCfNseq1ee3cJLBp0rH0djT.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1fFseB3A35TmXVVb9mz6e6bIMZ0.jpg', 'en', 'Glengarry Glen Ross', 'Crime', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'When an office full of Chicago real estate salesmen is given the news that all but the top two will be fired at the end of the week, the atmosphere begins to heat up. Shelley Levene, who has a sick daughter, does everything in his power to get better leads from his boss, John Williamson, but to no avail. When his coworker Dave Moss comes up with a plan to steal the leads, things get complicated for the tough-talking salesmen.', '1992-09-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_VrekKSuFto', 'James Foley', 'Al Pacino, Jack Lemmon, Alec Baldwin, Alan Arkin, Ed Harris');
