(689, 64682, 7.369, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tyxfCBQv6Ap74jcu3xd7aBiaa29.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/tb440cwQMRoVHnhYJlzlxfv1ikm.jpg', 'en', 'The Great Gatsby', 'Drama', 'Romance', NULL, 'An adaptation of F. Scott Fitzgerald\'s Long Island-set novel, where Midwesterner Nick Carraway is lured into the lavish world of his neighbor, Jay Gatsby. Soon enough, however, Carraway will see through the cracks of Gatsby\'s nouveau riche existence, where obsession, madness, and tragedy await.', '2013-05-09', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l6yANES3TMM', 'Baz Luhrmann', 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Tobey Maguire, Carey Mulligan, Joel Edgerton, Elizabeth Debicki'),
(690, 37799, 7.369, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/n0ybibhJtQ5icDqTp8eRytcIHJx.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cq9N64ucEtfIc3eMxNr1VzY9LH9.jpg', 'en', 'The Social Network', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'In 2003, Harvard undergrad and computer genius Mark Zuckerberg begins work on a new concept that eventually turns into the global social network known as Facebook. Six years later, he is one of the youngest billionaires ever, but Zuckerberg finds that his unprecedented success leads to both personal and legal complications when he ends up on the receiving end of two lawsuits, one involving his former friend.', '2010-10-01', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rBCNU0XT9GY', 'David Fincher', 'Jesse Eisenberg, Andrew Garfield, Armie Hammer, Justin Timberlake, Max Minghella'),
(691, 16307, 7.369, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wwtrXRL8SiOWxhwLEvw7iBgYh0g.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/53uHO73C09SrRzmcHvex3wY8gM6.jpg', 'en', 'The Wicker Man', 'Horror', NULL, NULL, 'Police sergeant Neil Howie is called to an island village in search of a missing girl whom the locals claim never existed. Stranger still, however, are the rituals that take place there.', '1973-12-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MXq-NuS24fg', 'Robin Hardy', 'Edward Woodward, Christopher Lee, Britt Ekland, Ingrid Pitt, Diane Cilento'),
(692, 4133, 7.368, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/yYZFVfk8aeMP4GxBSU9MTvqs9mJ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nCKpbN8SV6yAw4sgYVsnneZjbbZ.jpg', 'en', 'Blow', 'Crime', 'Drama', NULL, 'A boy named George Jung grows up in a struggling family in the 1950\'s. His mother nags at her husband as he is trying to make a living for the family. It is finally revealed that George\'s father cannot make a living and the family goes bankrupt. George does not want the same thing to happen to him, and his friend Tuna, in the 1960\'s, suggests that he deal marijuana. He is a big hit in California in the 1960\'s, yet he goes to jail, where he finds out about the wonders of cocaine. As a result, when released, he gets rich by bringing cocaine to America. However, he soon pays the price.', '2001-04-04', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hIx33TmN-IM', 'Ted Demme', 'Johnny Depp, Penélope Cruz, Franka Potente, Rachel Griffiths, Ray Liotta'),
(693, 80278, 7.368, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1kBYwWu24QKf47mumWEIAzo5tIu.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3Le4bZybmLinQp7m7KDP4LKngV4.jpg', 'en', 'The Impossible', 'Adventure', 'Drama', 'Thriller', 'In December 2004, close-knit family Maria, Henry and their three sons begin their winter vacation in Thailand. But the day after Christmas, the idyllic holiday turns into an incomprehensible nightmare when a terrifying roar rises from the depths of the sea, followed by a wall of black water that devours everything in its path. Though Maria and her family face their darkest hour, unexpected displays of kindness and courage ameliorate their terror.', '2012-09-09', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PaY8EeUYh10', 'J. A. Bayona', 'Naomi Watts, Ewan McGregor, Tom Holland, Samuel Joslin, Oaklee Pendergast'),
(694, 46838, 7.4, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/8shwLEDzajJGSfLgbpac8x8xn1U.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9WRhl49xB7NkdL7tdMR9CLMf5FQ.jpg', 'en', 'Tucker and Dale vs. Evil', 'Comedy', 'Horror', NULL, 'Two hillbillies are suspected of being killers by a group of paranoid college kids camping near the duo\'s West Virginian cabin. As the body count climbs, so does the fear and confusion as the college kids try to seek revenge against the pair.', '2010-01-22', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NdNpFoWrBDQ', 'Eli Craig', 'Alan Tudyk, Tyler Labine, Katrina Bowden, Philip Granger, Jesse Moss'),
(695, 11644, 7.367, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/weMW1wLzeagP3tw6BfmYf1iL7dz.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nk87CtgZ7wd86W37oJHGYAJbmLz.jpg', 'en', 'Blow Out', 'Thriller', 'Mystery', 'Crime', 'Jack Terry is a master sound recordist who works on grade-B horror movies. Late one evening, he is recording sounds for use in his movies when he hears something unexpected through his sound equipment and records it. Curiosity gets the better of him when the media become involved, and he begins to unravel the pieces of a nefarious conspiracy. As he struggles to survive against his shadowy enemies and expose the truth, he does not know whom he can trust.', '1981-07-24', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dgWfyFgEsO8', 'Brian De Palma', 'John Travolta, Nancy Allen, John Lithgow, Dennis Franz, Peter Boyden'),
(696, 560057, 7.366, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9Zfv4Ap1e8eKOYnZPtYaWhLkk0d.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wUwizGzbTk5CTiKBnE4Pq1MONwD.jpg', 'en', 'The Sea Beast', 'Animation', 'Adventure', 'Family', 'In an era when terrifying beasts roamed the seas, monster hunters were celebrated heroes. None were more beloved than the great Jacob Holland. But when young Maisie Brumble stows away on his fabled ship, he\'s saddled with an unexpected ally. Together they embark on an epic journey into uncharted waters and make history.', '2022-06-24', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P-E-IGQCsPo', 'Chris Williams', 'Karl Urban, Zaris-Angel Hator, Jared Harris, Marianne Jean-Baptiste, Benjamin Plessala'),
(697, 387426, 7.366, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pHlRr2MfjK77VIIAO7p0R4jhsJI.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1ycTOys6bzvt0XPnzSv8qYfrD0V.jpg', 'en', 'Okja', 'Adventure', 'Drama', 'Science Fiction', 'A young girl named Mija risks everything to prevent a powerful, multi-national company from kidnapping her best friend - a massive animal named Okja.', '2017-06-28', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AjCebKn4iic', 'Bong Joon-ho', 'Tilda Swinton, Ahn Seo-hyun, Paul Dano, Jake Gyllenhaal, Lily Collins'),
(698, 307081, 7.366, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/kSQ49Fi3NVTqGGXILmxV2T2pdkG.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1tXlUvfhLVjM5rZcN2783IhCkbu.jpg', 'en', 'Southpaw', 'Action', 'Drama', NULL, 'Billy \"The Great\" Hope, the reigning junior middleweight boxing champion, has an impressive career, a loving wife and daughter, and a lavish lifestyle. However, when tragedy strikes, Billy hits rock bottom, losing his family, his house and his manager. He soon finds an unlikely savior in Tick Willis, a former fighter who trains the city\'s toughest amateur boxers. With his future on the line, Hope fights to reclaim the trust of those he loves the most.', '2015-03-24', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mh2ebPxhoLs', 'Antoine Fuqua', 'Jake Gyllenhaal, Rachel McAdams, Forest Whitaker, Oona Laurence, 50 Cent'),
(699, 705996, 7.4, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/TDaXKGBqJUSbCQ9XjkrJs8GYuU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/y7efrL5RlIRsGfrhcaiP35V1x2g.jpg', 'ko', 'Decision to Leave', 'Thriller', 'Mystery', 'Romance', 'From a mountain peak in South Korea, a man plummets to his death. Did he jump, or was he pushed? When detective Hae-joon arrives on the scene, he begins to suspect the dead man’s wife Seo-rae. But as he digs deeper into the investigation, he finds himself trapped in a web of deception and desire.', '2022-06-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xL5bU-M_qEg', 'Park Chan-wook', 'Tang Wei, Park Hae-il, Lee Jung-hyun, Go Kyung-pyo, Park Yong-woo'),
(700, 81188, 7.365, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/sW4qOa9yF0Ikg7lppncQ0n5UhKX.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/46IGtYNjpIvQYRIQlb2X493Wh8x.jpg', 'en', 'Rise of the Guardians', 'Family', 'Animation', 'Fantasy', 'When an evil spirit known as Pitch lays down the gauntlet to take over the world, the immortal Guardians must join forces for the first time to protect the hopes, beliefs and imagination of children all over the world.', '2012-11-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aPLiBxhoug0', 'Peter Ramsey', 'Chris Pine, Alec Baldwin, Jude Law, Isla Fisher, Hugh Jackman'),
(701, 205220, 7.364, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/eBUv2GmGdXmCk1AaSOmyiu70hN8.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/eyn0vuN4IZjImE5Dws0iPhZrCMc.jpg', 'en', 'Philomena', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'A woman searches for her adult son, who was taken away from her decades ago when she was forced to live in a convent.', '2013-11-01', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a8WyFLsdtNw', 'Stephen Frears', 'Judi Dench, Steve Coogan, Sophie Kennedy Clark, Mare Winningham, Barbara Jefford'),
(702, 10024, 7.4, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/atRGqnG7pe0hZP97RWDLrT2hRGZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zpVMWiNJgcwHB0zIMGjXQMnSKPZ.jpg', 'en', 'My Sister\'s Keeper', 'Drama', NULL, NULL, 'Sara and Brian live an idyllic life with their young son and daughter. But their family is rocked by sudden, heartbreaking news that forces them to make a difficult and unorthodox choice in order to save their baby girl\'s life. The parents\' desperate decision raises both ethical and moral questions and rips away at the foundation of their relationship. Their actions ultimately set off a court case that threatens to tear the family apart, while revealing surprising truths that challenge everyone\'s perceptions of love and loyalty and give new meaning to the definition of healing.', '2009-06-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KGEDVTiI6E4', 'Nick Cassavetes', 'Cameron Diaz, Abigail Breslin, Sofia Vassilieva, Alec Baldwin, Jason Patric'),
(703, 417320, 7.363, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/qoNlGfQmFZ37Gf5fRBaCTLlOZtx.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/mLihPIodzSenkZtiUauDy4e9hRs.jpg', 'en', 'Descendants 2', 'Family', 'Fantasy', 'TV Movie', 'When the pressure to be royal becomes too much for Mal, she returns to the Isle of the Lost where her archenemy Uma, Ursula\'s daughter, has taken her spot as self-proclaimed queen.', '2017-07-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kmpm9c2hqvM', 'Kenny Ortega', 'Dove Cameron, Cameron Boyce, Sofia Carson, Booboo Stewart, Mitchell Hope'),
(704, 11901, 7.4, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/AjkJCFkqanK1OZqiHxc6Kl2wPQO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hUw44d6NAFd48xSCLkYb6GluXa7.jpg', 'en', 'High Plains Drifter', 'Western', 'Drama', 'Mystery', 'A gunfighting stranger comes to the small settlement of Lago. After gunning down three gunmen who tried to kill him, the townsfolk decide to hire the Stranger to hold off three outlaws who are on their way.', '1973-04-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=be2mIVxDrr8', 'Clint Eastwood', 'Clint Eastwood, Verna Bloom, Marianna Hill, Mitchell Ryan, Jack Ging'),
(705, 2252, 7.363, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dpiJWb4NrWgcOg2rusuLhDM0hTm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1ckHUJ6ztq5XJRKM2nIAW0UjJNH.jpg', 'en', 'Eastern Promises', 'Thriller', 'Crime', 'Mystery', 'A Russian teenager living in London dies during childbirth but leaves clues in her diary that could tie her child to a rape involving a violent Russian mob family.', '2007-09-14', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ifilHp3_dWQ', 'David Cronenberg', 'Viggo Mortensen, Naomi Watts, Vincent Cassel, Armin Mueller-Stahl, Sinéad Cusack'),
(706, 663260, 7.362, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nNY5YnqCsMEggz2Z0kCl4Fclc1N.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/1KIWr83GPeO1Z54lndzs2H4OoBe.jpg', 'fr', 'Black Box', 'Mystery', 'Thriller', 'Drama', 'Mathieu is a young and talented black box analyst on a mission to solve the reason behind the deadly crash of a brand new aircraft. Yet, when the case is closed by authorities, Mathieu cannot help but sense there is something wrong with the evidence. As he listens to the tracks again, he starts detecting some seriously disturbing details. Could the tape have been modified? Going against his boss\' orders, Mathieu begins his own rogue investigation - an obsessional and dangerous quest for truth that will quickly threaten far more than his career...', '2021-09-08', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_dooRWLaKns', 'Yann Gozlan', 'Pierre Niney, Lou de Laâge, André Dussollier, Sébastien Pouderoux, Olivier Rabourdin'),
(707, 2757, 7.362, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ffEmHQAiD0m5dEQ6rlsuA9vlllW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jqz8kodfEQTrNxLkT1XiyM0gqte.jpg', 'en', 'Adaptation.', 'Comedy', 'Crime', 'Drama', 'Nicolas Cage is Charlie Kaufman, a confused L.A. screenwriter overwhelmed by feelings of inadequacy, sexual frustration, self-loathing, and by the screenwriting ambitions of his freeloading twin brother Donald. While struggling to adapt \"The Orchid Thief,\" by Susan Orlean, Kaufman\'s life spins from pathetic to bizarre. The lives of Kaufman, Orlean\'s book, become strangely intertwined as each one\'s search for passion collides with the others\'.', '2002-12-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pK5jYt9QNIY', 'Spike Jonze', 'Nicolas Cage, Meryl Streep, Chris Cooper, Tilda Swinton, Jay Tavare'),
(708, 13183, 7.337, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zcCGhnlO4qi8ZqunUHAnYkwUtRX.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dH7ia3vtkYCa3CBvDnvVjqm9uiQ.jpg', 'en', 'Watchmen', 'Mystery', 'Action', 'Science Fiction', 'In a gritty and alternate 1985, the glory days of costumed vigilantes have been brought to a close by a government crackdown. But after one of the masked veterans is brutally murdered, an investigation into the killer is initiated. The reunited heroes set out to prevent their own destruction, but in doing so they uncover a sinister plot that puts all of humanity in grave danger.', '2009-03-04', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=89xoXmHgG00', 'Zack Snyder', 'Malin Åkerman, Patrick Wilson, Billy Crudup, Matthew Goode, Jackie Earle Haley'),
(709, 438148, 7.336, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wKiOkZTN9lUUUNZLmtnwubZYONg.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uMSxXLfH7v30gRNBqsQaSP3yqX5.jpg', 'en', 'Minions: The Rise of Gru', 'Animation', 'Comedy', 'Family', 'A fanboy of a supervillain supergroup known as the Vicious 6, Gru hatches a plan to become evil enough to join them, with the backup of his followers, the Minions.', '2022-06-29', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HhIl_XJ-OGA', 'Kyle Balda', 'Steve Carell, Pierre Coffin, Alan Arkin, Taraji P. Henson, Michelle Yeoh'),
(710, 377, 7.3, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wGTpGGRMZmyFCcrY2YoxVTIBlli.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/g9ROrZey0JYp7kf8DoAyZtKnObj.jpg', 'en', 'A Nightmare on Elm Street', 'Horror', NULL, NULL, 'Teenagers in a small town are dropping like flies, apparently in the grip of mass hysteria causing their suicides. A cop\'s daughter, Nancy Thompson, traces the cause to child molester Fred Krueger, who was burned alive by angry parents many years before. Krueger has now come back in the dreams of his killers\' children, claiming their lives as his revenge. Nancy and her boyfriend, Glen, must devise a plan to lure the monster out of the realm of nightmares and into the real world...', '1984-10-31', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kPpmJ7azGSY', 'Wes Craven', 'Heather Langenkamp, John Saxon, Ronee Blakley, Amanda Wyss, Jsu Garcia'),
(711, 9571, 7.333, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/msG9awbLhVZwv1Eh9Ge7SofMexW.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/9Vygw4sIUyMZ3kY5mUmk1ccsDJc.jpg', 'en', 'Dazed and Confused', 'Comedy', 'Drama', NULL, 'The adventures of a group of Texas teens on their last day of school in 1976, centering on student Randall Floyd, who moves easily among stoners, jocks and geeks. Floyd is a star athlete, but he also likes smoking weed, which presents a conundrum when his football coach demands he sign a \"no drugs\" pledge.', '1993-09-24', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uzDPw5N8d_0', 'Richard Linklater', 'Jason London, Matthew McConaughey, Joey Lauren Adams, Rory Cochrane, Wiley Wiggins'),
(712, 2841, 7.335, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/t73m7lX0eFYDjlB1Gcb7r3S5Yt.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/xdxnl5x8it3vLIaivaMP4h5NJNq.jpg', 'fr', 'A Very Long Engagement', 'Drama', 'Romance', 'War', 'Young Frenchwoman Mathilde searches for the truth about her missing fiancé, lost during World War I, and learns many unexpected things along the way. The love of her life is gone. But she refuses to believe he\'s gone forever — and she needs to know for sure.', '2004-10-27', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2HJXPvM1y2E', 'Jean-Pierre Jeunet', 'Audrey Tautou, Gaspard Ulliel, Dominique Pinon, Chantal Neuwirth, André Dussollier'),
(713, 9385, 7.334, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7cZQZOYZFJcLjZnxWjO5PcUtmDZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/fRMpmzN4GdLRDrADukxHtuyioqB.jpg', 'fr', 'The Twelve Tasks of Asterix', 'Family', 'Animation', 'Comedy', 'Asterix and Obelix depart on an adventure to complete twelve impossible tasks to prove to Caesar that they are as strong as the Gods. You\'ll roar with laughter as they outwit, outrun, and generally outrage the very people who are trying to prove them \"only human\".', '1976-06-26', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1WVGszqwkkI', 'René Goscinny, Henri Gruel', 'Roger Carel, Jacques Morel, Pierre Tornade, Henri Labussière, Jean Martinelli'),
(714, 576845, 7.333, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/n1ZRmjlk1BJTY7aASqACfPAaLn2.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/brOCMGntRbx9SKzeQk1Aisu6vXz.jpg', 'en', 'Last Night in Soho', 'Mystery', 'Thriller', 'Horror', 'A young girl, passionate about fashion design, is mysteriously able to enter the 1960s where she encounters her idol, a dazzling wannabe singer. But 1960s London is not what it seems, and time seems to be falling apart with shady consequences.', '2021-10-21', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XgNrL4Kf7yU', 'Edgar Wright', 'Thomasin McKenzie, Anya Taylor-Joy, Matt Smith, Rita Tushingham, Michael Ajao'),
(715, 82695, 7.333, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/6CuzBs2Lb8At7qQr64mLXg2RYRb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/jd3Z2sAPDavjRxFhfOak6kCrUIG.jpg', 'en', 'Les Misérables', 'History', 'Drama', NULL, 'An adaptation of the successful stage musical based on Victor Hugo\'s classic novel set in 19th-century France. Jean Valjean, a man imprisoned for stealing bread, must flee a relentless policeman named Javert. The pursuit consumes both men\'s lives, and soon Valjean finds himself in the midst of the student revolutions in France.', '2012-12-18', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=28sHoKcpugw', 'Tom Hooper', 'Hugh Jackman, Russell Crowe, Anne Hathaway, Amanda Seyfried, Sacha Baron Cohen'),
(716, 1429, 7.333, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uW7tTRElr2tRhmAVESzvHy4ByXg.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/t31mKP1dIzUiy0yapCje0vdf2ZY.jpg', 'en', '25th Hour', 'Crime', 'Drama', NULL, 'In New York City in the days following the events of 9/11, Monty Brogan is a convicted drug dealer about to start a seven-year prison sentence, and his final hours of freedom are devoted to hanging out with his closest buddies and trying to prepare his girlfriend for his extended absence.', '2002-12-19', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YVHY9nIPo6s', 'Spike Lee', 'Edward Norton, Philip Seymour Hoffman, Barry Pepper, Rosario Dawson, Anna Paquin'),
(717, 470, 7.333, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/hdS0to9nUpgK0Zm1bZAF6BWRae7.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/5SgrtPH6kBmmHao0PofxpvOYfWC.jpg', 'en', '21 Grams', 'Drama', 'Crime', 'Thriller', 'Paul Rivers, an ailing mathematician lovelessly married to an English émigré; Christina Peck, an upper-middle-class suburban housewife and mother of two girls; and Jack Jordan, a born-again ex-con, are brought together by a terrible accident that changes their lives.', '2003-09-06', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x_tPi8pYzSw', 'Alejandro González Iñárritu', 'Sean Penn, Naomi Watts, Danny Huston, Carly Nahon, Claire Pakis'),
(718, 34647, 7.332, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/krKnsfvSJM1PL40tLicRhVQ6kuG.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/h0L4AI7qx0x5rJu9sbpSHYjw0Ln.jpg', 'en', 'Enter the Void', 'Fantasy', 'Drama', NULL, 'This psychedelic tour of life after death is seen entirely from the point of view of Oscar, a young American drug dealer and addict living in Tokyo with his prostitute sister, Linda. When Oscar is killed by police during a bust gone bad, his spirit journeys from the past -- where he sees his parents before their deaths -- to the present -- where he witnesses his own autopsy -- and then to the future, where he looks out for his sister from beyond the grave.', '2009-06-17', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j8SKVcDc4po', 'Gaspar Noé', 'Paz de la Huerta, Nathaniel Brown, Cyril Roy, Olly Alexander, Ed Spear'),
(719, 626735, 7.331, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/zHQy4h36WwuCetKS7C3wcT1hkgA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/cGnaZm6EQOJESde3Vv4v53Zk4gN.jpg', 'en', 'Dog', 'Drama', 'Comedy', NULL, 'An army ranger and his dog embark on a road trip along the Pacific Coast Highway to attend a friend\'s funeral.', '2022-02-17', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JL6p4IAI23Y', 'Channing Tatum, Reid Carolin', 'Channing Tatum, Aavi Haas, Ryder McLaughlin, Luke Forbes, Darren Keilan'),
