(764, 57212, 7.311, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/nF66DU2zPLFb9CxDQNSNX2RgNaq.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/64YOcrslrijllDRCpQvXkSKvXQV.jpg', 'en', 'War Horse', 'War', 'History', 'Adventure', 'On the brink of the First World War, Albert\'s beloved horse Joey is sold to the Cavalry by his father. Against the backdrop of the Great War, Joey begins an odyssey full of danger, joy, and sorrow, and he transforms everyone he meets along the way. Meanwhile, Albert, unable to forget his equine friend, searches the battlefields of France to find Joey and bring him home.', '2011-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kEhmx28Tbek', 'Steven Spielberg', 'Jeremy Irvine, Peter Mullan, Emily Watson, Niels Arestrup, David Thewlis'),
(765, 1265, 7.31, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/3xFxGodKPMFLheS8rujFSmLfcq4.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/o4mQHoP8LExn2Q9dn16OGqHvaiK.jpg', 'en', 'Bridge to Terabithia', 'Adventure', 'Drama', 'Family', 'Jesse Aarons trained all summer to become the fastest runner in school. So he\'s very upset when newcomer Leslie Burke outruns him and everyone else. Despite this and other differences including that she\'s rich, he\'s poor, she\'s a city girl, and he\'s a country boy the two become fast friends. Together they create Terabithia, a land of monsters, trolls, ogres, and giants where they rule as king and queen.', '2007-02-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T2TDSEG57hI', 'Gábor Csupó', 'Josh Hutcherson, AnnaSophia Robb, Zooey Deschanel, Robert Patrick, Bailee Madison'),
(766, 7340, 7.31, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/uc3OvgmbnYaS5Y0BOjSmC1EmSz1.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/wm8eyF38AekA9ZGT7TGeqHHk5OY.jpg', 'en', 'Carrie', 'Horror', 'Thriller', NULL, 'An awkward, telekinetic teenage girl\'s lonely life is dominated by relentless bullying at school and an oppressive religious fanatic mother at home. When her tormentors pull a humiliating prank at the senior prom, she unleashes a horrifying chaos on everyone, leaving nothing but destruction in her wake.', '1976-11-03', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j9Mg-GRS46Y', 'Brian De Palma', 'Sissy Spacek, Piper Laurie, Amy Irving, William Katt, Nancy Allen'),
(767, 801, 7.31, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rcod81d34X1avhRIKBOQ4BsHtYZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/l04cyHUP6PCAozc2GMEHPguu7AN.jpg', 'en', 'Good Morning, Vietnam', 'Comedy', 'Drama', 'War', 'A disk jockey goes to Vietnam to work for the Armed Forces Radio Service. While he becomes popular among the troops, his superiors disapprove of his humour.', '1987-12-23', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JnBXv3W0arQ', 'Barry Levinson', 'Robin Williams, Forest Whitaker, Tom T. Tran, Chintara Sukapatana, Bruno Kirby'),
