(785, 11886, 7.3, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/alcY9jZBgKw9OB7hiPYVNvh03Sb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/b1JNEmsm73g16gR0U20D12pBR3w.jpg', 'en', 'Robin Hood', 'Animation', 'Family', NULL, 'With King Richard off to the Crusades, Prince John and his slithering minion, Sir Hiss, set about taxing Nottingham\'s citizens with support from the corrupt sheriff - and staunch opposition by the wily Robin Hood and his band of merry men.', '1973-11-08', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z4rLod7TBEY', 'Wolfgang Reitherman', 'Brian Bedford, Phil Harris, Andy Devine, Monica Evans, Peter Ustinov'),
