(888, 109445, 7.247, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/itAKcobTYGpYT8Phwjd8c9hleTo.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/rj58WQ9ImI0mYDptXdM7euX1Wjt.jpg', 'en', 'Frozen', 'Animation', 'Family', 'Adventure', 'Young princess Anna of Arendelle dreams about finding true love at her sister Elsa’s coronation. Fate takes her on a dangerous journey in an attempt to end the eternal winter that has fallen over the kingdom. She\'s accompanied by ice delivery man Kristoff, his reindeer Sven, and snowman Olaf. On an adventure where she will find out what friendship, courage, family, and true love really means.', '2013-11-20', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TbQm5doF_Uc', 'Jennifer Lee, Chris Buck', 'Kristen Bell, Idina Menzel, Jonathan Groff, Josh Gad, Santino Fontana'),
(889, 9078, 7.2, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/dYQhKThGXl3xQv71Ysw0RSmVmBA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7jvHnJcCSfk8bhjy9U78HZ9jzkC.jpg', 'en', 'The Sword in the Stone', 'Animation', 'Family', 'Fantasy', 'Wart is a young boy who aspires to be a knight\'s squire. On a hunting trip he falls in on Merlin, a powerful but amnesiac wizard who has plans for him beyond mere squiredom. He starts by trying to give him an education, believing that once one has an education, one can go anywhere. Needless to say, it doesn\'t quite work out that way.', '1963-12-25', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UI57RCDMgVM', 'Wolfgang Reitherman', 'Sebastian Cabot, Karl Swenson, Junius Matthews, Martha Wentworth, Norman Alden'),
(890, 642885, 7.246, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/7ze7YNmUaX81ufctGqt0AgHxRtL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/ml8YBTJq7UkALfI022FWscCQuQW.jpg', 'en', 'Hocus Pocus 2', 'Fantasy', 'Comedy', 'Family', '29 years since the Black Flame Candle was last lit, the 17th-century Sanderson sisters are resurrected, and they are looking for revenge. Now it\'s up to three high school students to stop the ravenous witches from wreaking a new kind of havoc on Salem before dawn on All Hallow\'s Eve.', '2022-09-30', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=idc0EOmKr30', 'Anne Fletcher', 'Bette Midler, Sarah Jessica Parker, Kathy Najimy, Whitney Peak, Belissa Escobedo'),
