(895, 14202, 7.245, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/k41IvHDLgZO2ae7RuU77wQjScIj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/j94REWD9CFfN8accJX572RoQUj9.jpg', 'en', 'The Painted Veil', 'Romance', 'Drama', NULL, 'A British medical doctor fights a cholera outbreak in a small Chinese village, while also being trapped at home in a loveless marriage to an unfaithful wife.', '2006-12-09', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1oevR8c35Qk', 'John Curran', 'Edward Norton, Naomi Watts, Liev Schreiber, Diana Rigg, Toby Jones'),
