(909, 345920, 7.232, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/pVIAPiIvHcitgXV8BA7uTyCcEuk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/iovi35nPfjbYTw2gRo7uImWblRU.jpg', 'en', 'Collateral Beauty', 'Drama', 'Romance', NULL, 'Retreating from life after a tragedy, a man questions the universe by writing to Love, Time and Death. Receiving unexpected answers, he begins to see how these things interlock and how even loss can reveal moments of meaning and beauty.', '2016-12-15', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w1tfLWxcEzw', 'David Frankel', 'Will Smith, Edward Norton, Kate Winslet, Michael Peña, Helen Mirren'),
